CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AC'), course_name='自動化工程', course_teacher='蔡明忠', course_type=1, course_discription='1.自動化概論。2.自動化系統所需元件、裝置。3.伺服控制與程序控制。4.微電腦控制界面。5.自動化組裝、物流、倉儲。6.電腦通訊與監控。7.電腦整合製造。//1.Introduction <br>2.Automation keywords<br>3.Automated elements<br>4.Automated controller(PC, PLC/PAC)<br>5.CNC<br>6.Molding process automation<br>7.Rapid Prototyping (RP) automation<br>8.Automated assembly <br>9.Robotics automation<br>10.ASRS & FMS <br>11.CIM /CAD/CAM/ E-automation (Manufacturing Support System)<br>12.SCADA & SECS  <br>13.System Modeling methods<br>14.Case study: Semiconductor/FPD manufacturing automation process<br>15.Paper reading & Video', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AC5007701')
