CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='色彩學', course_teacher='吳榮梅', course_type=1, course_discription='課程主要內容包含 1.色彩原理 2.作品案例分析 3.色彩應用與設計。本課程以專題分析討論的方式，引導學生了解色彩的設計心理歷程與應用，透過繪畫、建築、電影…等多元案例解析與實驗創作，進而提升設計相關領域對色彩運用的敏銳度與表現力。//The course consists of three parts as below. 1. Lecture on theory of Chromatics. 2. Case study. 3. Professional practice of color scheme. This project provides an opportunity for students to further study on principles of Chromatics. The course puts special emphasis on the application of these principles to design and the psychology of color scheme. Through various approaches to theoretical study and case study, students are expected to apply in practice their knowledge and experience of the specialist concerns in the creative design.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3119701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='社區規劃與設計', course_teacher='邱韻祥', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程教授”社區規劃與設計”之理論、案例與實務操作，學習如何在由下而上、參與式決策的過程，發掘各方(stakeholders)的利基與共同價值，以此建立溝通基礎，配合人文與物理環境的調查，在社區與小區域的尺度，實踐空間規劃與設計專業，達到強化鄰里與社區功能，團結在地社會網絡，增進在地宜居性(livability)的目標', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3120701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='室內空間設計(一)', course_teacher='呂惠瑛', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程著重於以室內空間繪圖表現訓練為主，輔以室內空間設計原則、人因工程、燈光色彩、材質運用等教學，探討室內設計的基本原理與空間規劃的方法。課程內容依序為：<br>1. 室內空間設計方法(理論)：室內空間設計原則及概念介紹、設計圖面繪製方法及應注意事項。<br>2. 室內設計圖說(課堂操作)：依前一堂理論課程內容，於課堂上實際操作演練。以達成設計構想至實踐的一致性訓練。//This course is focused on the training of presentation for interior design.   The training is giving upon on principles of spatial design, human-factors engineering, lighting and colors and using of materials. The aim of the course is to introduce students how to achieve the detail of drawing in the end of design phase and realize the further process in detail design phase. The contents of the course in order are blow this:<br>1.Design theory; to introduce the strategies of practice associated with theory and concept of interior design, methods of drawing and matters needing attention <br>2.Actual practice; the training is according to the contents of course preceding, actual operation in the class, to achieve the training from design conception to the practice.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3121701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='數位建築模型', course_teacher='施宣光', course_type=1, course_discription='1.數位建築設計與工程案例<br>2.參數化模型的工具<br>3.建築資訊模型<br>4.Generative Components介紹<br>5.Model-based approach<br>6.Script-based approach//1.Case study – digital architecture design and constuction<br>2.Tools for parametric modeling<br>3.Building information model<br>4.Introduction to Generative Components<br>5.Model-based approach of building model<br>6.Script-based approach of building model', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3124701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='工程估價', course_teacher='吳海偉(待)', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程的內容包括：工程估價的基本概念，工程估價的方法，土再、模板、鋼筋、混凝土、粉刷等工程數量的計算，並討論各種影響工程造價的因素。//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3204701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='環境控制系統(二)', course_teacher='鄭政利', course_type=0, course_discription='課程共計一學年，本學期的主要內容為建築設備的特性，包括電氣設備、空調設備、水環境設備等三大部份，並加入全球與能源環境的探討。課程內容包括：能源總論、電力設備、電力配線系統、輸送設備、空調原理與負荷分析、空調設備、空調方式、空調管線系統、空調節能、水資源與保水、水質與用水、給水設備、排水設備、污水與廢棄物處理、節水、透濕與結露防止。//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD3205301')
