CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='AD'), course_name='公共建築規劃設計實務', course_teacher='葉宏安', course_type=1, course_discription='一、概述<br>二、使用建築空間需求有關「定性」與「定量」之擬定<br>三、公共建築自「構想」、「規劃」至「設計」各作業階段之分際，合理之作業時程與實質設計約30%成果之審議機制。<br>四、除有關法令或技術規則外，公共建築「因地制宜」、「地竟其利」、「物竟其用」所涉「人本」、「服務」理念以及落實「節能」、「事後維護」之規畫設計。<br>五、建築與土木、結構、機電、給排污水…等專技於規劃設計之「互動」與「整合」。<br>六、近年多種不同屬性公共建築之規劃設計取向以及「不宜」之案情探討:<br>1.學校、宿舍 2.公共圖書館 3.集會、展演、活動中心…等建築 4.運動場/館 5.大眾運輸、交通…等建築 6.醫事建築 7.其他(工商綜合區民生有關大型購物中心、非建築之公共設施、地下街…等)//1.INTRODUCTION<br>2.THE STUDY OF THE REQUIREMENT OF RELATIVE ROOM SPACE WITH REGARD TO SUITABLE FEATURE AND DIMENSIONS.<br>3.THE DIFFERENTIATION STARTING FROM THE STAGE OF FEASIBILIY STUDY VIA PLANNING TO DESIGN WITH REASONABLE WORK TIME RESPECTIVELY,AND THE MECHANISM OF THE OFFICIAL REVIEWING ABOUT 30% DESIGN PERFORMANCE.<br>4.THE PUBLIC WORKS IN THE FIELD OF ARCHITECTURE REGARDING TO THE ADEQUATE APPLICATION AND ADVANTAGE OF THE RELATIVE SITE ACCORDINGLY AND MAKING GOODS OF GREAT USE WITH THE SENSE OF “HUMAN NATURE”AND”SERVICES”,AND THE EFFECTIVE”MAINTENANCE AFTERWARD” WITH “ENERGY SAVING” IN ADDITION TO THE EXISTING BUILDING CODES OR CRITERIA.<br>5.THE INTERACTION AND INTEGRATION BETWEEN THE ARCHITECTURE,CIVIL ENGINEEING,STRUCTURE,ELECTRIC & MECHENIC ENGINEERING AND PLUMBIN IN PLANING AND DESIGN.<br>6.THE STATUS QUO OF SEVERAL PUBUC WORKS IN THE FIELD OF ARCHITECTURE ABOUR THE ESSENTIAL PLANING AND DESIG WITH THE AVOIDANCE OF MISTAKES AS FOLLOWING:<br>?SCHOOL,DORM…ETC?PUBLIC LIBRARY?AUDITORUM,CONCERTOR RECITAL HALL,BLACK BOX…ETC?GYM,STADIUM,FIELD WITH BLEACHE?TRANSPORT STATION…ETC?GENERAL HOSPITAL,POLY CLINIC…ETC?OTHERS(CONVENTION,SHOPPING CENTER,VERSATI', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=AD5232701')
