CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='國際金融', course_teacher='王健全', course_type=1, course_discription='由國際收支平衡表開始，並說明戰後國際貨幣制度的演變，有關外匯市場及其均衡，遠期外匯理論，國際金融市場，國民所得，對外貿易並分析匯率理論的派別及分析開放經濟的總體經濟政策。//The purpose of this course is twofolds.  First, we introduce International Finance theory including foreign exchange market, foreign exchange rate determination and international finance system.  Second, we cover some current issues related with international finance such as Asian Financial Crisis, RMB’s appreciation and its impact on Taiwan’s economy.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA4704701')
