CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='投資管理', course_teacher='徐中琦', course_type=1, course_discription='網路的發展已使得投資資訊的取得更為豐富與便利，在正確的投資觀念下〈同時考慮風險與報酬〉如何運用各項投資工具〈股票、債券、基金、期貨、選擇權、外匯、黃金〉與投資分析〈基本分析與技術分析〉以獲取合理的報酬將是21世紀不可或缺的理財課題。//The development of the internet has help people to obtain abundant financial information very easily. Therefore, how to use varied investment instruments such as stocks, bonds, mutual funds, futures, options, foreign exchange, gold and fundamental/technical analyses to obtain reasonable profits become an important topic that needs to be studied further to advance our<br>understanding of investment management in the 21 St century.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA5206701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='財務管理', course_teacher='徐中琦', course_type=1, course_discription='最佳投資決策分析，風險與報酬，資本預算與風險，公司理財與市場效率，股利政策與資本結構﹑選擇權﹑債務融通等。//This course examines the financing decision, investment decision, and risk management made by financial manager. What has to be done correctly by managers to enhance the company value is also addressed. Emphasis is place on the concepts and techniques of financial management problems. By applying theory to practical issue, student will conduct real-world cases studies in financial statements analysis, capital budgeting decision and valuation.<br>1.To guide student with the understanding of the nature of fundamentals of accounting and financial planning<br>2.To obtain the skill of financial ratio analysis and dictate the potential flaw on financial statements<br>3.To learn the capital budgeting decision methods and their relative strengths and weaknesses<br>4.To understand the meaning of corporate financing decisions and its impact on firm performance.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA5300701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='人工智慧與管理個案研討', course_teacher='張譯尹', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程首先從人工智慧的觀點探討對管理帶來的影響與解決方案，其次概述智慧科技如何協助管理的個案。接著將實用Mplus軟體模擬解決方案<br>並透過實地參訪，與學員共同構思運用人工智慧與管理協作的可行方案。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA5411701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='策略管理', course_teacher='劉邦典', course_type=1, course_discription='1.策略與競爭 2.市場競爭型態與策略 3.影響策略制訂的因素-市場需求特徵 4.影響市場策略制訂的因素-技術特徵因素 5.先進者的優勢策略 6.品牌策略 7.台灣產品形象提升策略 8.垂直整合與外包策略 9.策略與賽局理論 10.策略應用 11.定位策略 12.搶佔先機策略//With the perspectives of strategic management, we seek to understand why enterprises chose certain strategies under some circumstances with respect to rivalry competition and environment factors.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA5501701')
