CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='BA'), course_name='組織理論', course_teacher='鄭仁偉', course_type=1, course_discription='訓練學生以嚴謹之數學模型分析各種組織管理問題；由GAME THEORY學習到策略思考的方法及策略管理；分析企業在不確定性及風險環境之下的運作。//This course bases on the evolution of the various organizational theories to discuss organizational structure design, as well as other factors that interact with the organizational restructuring, such as environmental change, technical complexity, organization size, power, communication, organization culture etc. Emphasizes how the many internal and external factors that shapes a particular architecture. Students will also demonstrate their grasp of organizational theory by developing and presenting the future research direction.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=BA7805701')
