CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='工程數學(一)', course_teacher='蔡大翔', course_type=0, course_discription='介紹工程上的基本數學方法。內容包括 常微分方程式的分析解法、拉氏轉換、向量空間、矩陣及線性轉換等。//Chapter 1 First-order differential equations<br>1.1 Separable equations<br>1.2  Linear equations<br>1.3 Exact equations<br>1.4  Integrating factors<br>1.5  Homogeneous, Bernoulli, Riccati equations<br>1.6    Applications of first-order differential equations<br>Chapter 2 Linear second-order differential equations<br>2.1 The linear second-order equation<br>2.2 Reduction of order<br>2.3 The constant coefficient case<br>2.4 The nonhomogeneous equation – involving variation of parameters, undetermined coefficients, the principle of superposition.<br>2.5 Spring motion – involving unforced motion, forced motion, resonance, beats, analogy with an electrical circuit.<br>2.6 Euler’s differential equation<br>Chapter 3 Laplace transform<br>3.1 Definitions and notations<br>3.2 Solution of initial value problems<br>3.3 Shifting and the Heaviside function<br>3.4 Convolution<br>3.5 Impulse and the Delta function<br>3.6 Solution of systems<br>3.7 Polynomial coefficients<br>Chapter 6 Vector and vector spaces<br>6.1 Vectors in 2D and 3D<br>6.2 The dot product<br>6.3 The cross product<br>6.4 The vector space<br>6.5 Orthogonalization<br>Chapter 11 Vector analysis<br>11.1 Vector functions of one variable<br>11.2 Velocity and curvature<br>11.3 Vector fields and streamlines<br>11.4The gradient field<br>11.5 Divergence and curl<br>Chapter 12 Vector integral calculus (if time permits)<br>12.1 Linear integrals<br>12.2 Green theorem', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH2000301')
