CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='單元操作與輸送現象(二)', course_teacher='何明樺', course_type=0, course_discription='//* Steady-State Heat Transfer<br>* Basic mechanisms<br>* Heat conduction<br>* Forced convection and Natural convection<br>* Boiling and condensation<br>* Heat exchangers<br>* Radiation heat transfer<br>* Special heat transfer coefficient<br>* Dimensional analysis<br>* Unsteady-State Heat Transfer<br>* Systems with negligible internal resistance<br>* Unsteady-state heat conduction<br>* Differential eqn. of energy of change<br>* Boundary-layer flow and turbulence in heat transfer<br>* Steady-State Mass Transfer<br>* Introduction to mass transfer<br>* Molecular diffusion in gases<br>* Molecular diffusion in liquids<br>* Molecular diffusion in solids<br>* Unsteady-State Mass Transfer<br>* Convective mass-transfer coefficient<br>* Mass transfer to suspensions of small particles<br>* Diffusion + convection + chemical reaction<br>* Diffusion of gases in porous solids and capillaries<br>* Dimensional analysis<br>  Boundary-layer flow and turbulence in heat transfer', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH2206301')
