CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='輸送現象', course_teacher='未  定', course_type=0, course_discription='課程包括化工單元操作及輸送現象，講述動量、 能量、質量之傳遞原理及應用，各類裝置之設計、構造及操作，含流體及固體之輸送裝置、熱傳遞裝置、精製、混合與分離裝置。//講述流體及固體內動量,?量及質量,如何進行傳遞原理及應用.本課程為一年課程,亦即分成上.下學期,則講授較高深的熱傳部份及質量在流體內分子的擴散及流體內本身物質及兩種物質如何進行相傳遞以及較高深之兩種或兩種以上物質加上反應前後之質傳現象．', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH3202301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='化工熱力學', course_teacher='李明哲', course_type=0, course_discription='由化工觀點探討熱力學，內容包括第一、第二定律、實際流體氣體和溶液之熱力性質、相平衡以及化學反應平衡等。//Thermodynamics is one of the core courses in chemical engineering. Basic principles of thermodynamics will be introduced systematically in the course as well as their engineering applications, particularly various types of energy flow and the concept of equilibrium. Topics covered in the course include basic introduction, mass balance, energy balance, entropy balance, properties of real fluids, equilibrium of one-component system, equilibrium of multi-component ystem, Gibbes free energy of mixtures and the estimation of fugacity. It is fundamental and essential for separation processes, reactor design, and process design.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH3203301')
