CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='高分子化學', course_teacher='王孟菊', course_type=1, course_discription='高分子化合物的物理性質、游離基、離子聚合等理論，機能性高分子合成、環化及縮合聚合反應、凝膠作用理論、共聚合理論之研討。//1.Basic principles & 2.Molecular weight and polymer solutions <br>3.Chemical structure and polymer morphology & <br>4.Chemical structure and polymer properties<br>5.Evaluation, characterization, and analysis of polymer <br>6.Free radical polymerization<br>7.Ionic polymerization<br>8.Vinyl polymerization with complex coordination catalysts<br>9.Reactions of vinyl polymers <br>10.Step-reaction and ring-opening polymerization<br>11.Polyethers, polysulfides, and related polymers<br>12.Polyesters<br>13.Polyamides and related polymers<br>14.Phenol-, urea-, and melamine-formaldehyde polymers<br>15.Heterocyclic polymers<br>16.Inorganic and partially inorganic polymers<br>17.Miscellaneous organic polymers<br>18.Natrual polymers', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH3207701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='化工熱力學', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=0, course_discription='Thermodynamics is the science of energy. Energy evaluation is one important aspect in chemical engineering. Basic principles of thermodynamics will be introduced systematically in the course as well as their engineering applications, particularly various types of energy flow and the concept of equilibrium. Topics covered in the course include basic introduction, mass balance, energy balance, entropy balance, properties of real fluids, equilibrium of one-component system, equilibrium of multi-component system, Gibbs free energy of mixtures and the estimation of fugacity. It is fundamental and essential for separation processes, reactor design, and process design.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH3213301')
