CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='奈米化學', course_teacher='陳良益', course_type=1, course_discription='在本課程中將說明材料進入奈米的領域時所造成特性上的轉變，同時介紹目前以化學如何進行奈米材料的製作、分析與科技的結合。<br><br>1. 奈米材料特性簡介          2. 日常生活中的奈米化學<br>3. 奈米材料的製作法與應用    4. 奈米圖案化技術與蝕刻的發展<br>5. 光子晶體簡介與其應用      6. 奈米材料自組裝技術之發展//In this course, we will compare the characteristics of nanoscale materials including 2-D, 1-D and 0-D nanomaterials, with bulk materials.  Besides, we also introduce how to apply chemical methods on the fabrication of nanomaterials.<br><br>1. Introduction of nanomaterials<br>2. Nanochemistry in the life<br>3. Fabrication of nanomaterials<br>4. Development of nano-patterning and lithography<br>5. Photonic and its applications<br>6. Nanomaterials self assembly.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH4110701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='程序設計', course_teacher='邱昱誠', course_type=0, course_discription='以單元操作、化工熱力學及反應工程的原理，教導學生如何從基本的質能平衡設計複雜的化工廠。內容包括概念設計、基本設計、細部設計以及整合設計。同時介紹如何從整廠設計之中回收資源、節省能源以及減少污染。//(1)Strategy for process analysis and optimization (Yao-Husan Tseng)<br>Chapter 2 Engineering Economics (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 3 Economic Decision Making: Design of a Solvent Recovery System (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 9 Cost Diagram and the Quick Screening of Process Alternatives (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 10 Preliminary Process Optimization (Douglas, 1988)<br>Appendix E Cost Data (Douglas, 1988)<br><br>(2)Conceptual design and process simulation (I-Lung Chien)<br>Chapter 4 Input Information and Batch versus Continuous (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 5 Input-Output Structure of the Flowsheet (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 6 Recycle Structure of the Flowsheet (Douglas, 1988)<br>Chapter 7 Separation System (Douglas, 1988)<br>          Introduction to Process Simulation with Demonstration of Aspen Plus (Handout)<br><br>(3)technology of clean process and fluid physical property(Ming-Jer Lee)<br>Chapter 27 Inherent Safety (Smith, 2005)<br>Chapter 28 Clean Process Technology (Smith, 2005)<br>Chapter 8 Heat-Exchanger Networks (Doug', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH4205301')
