CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='高分子物性', course_teacher='邱昱誠', course_type=1, course_discription='探討聚合物的一般特性，介紹聚合物之組成與結構，對其物性與機械性質之影響。//Syllabus<br>Week 1 (9/18,18,19)    Introduction to Polymer Science (Chap. 1)<br>Week 2 (9/25,25,26)    Chain Structure and Configuration (Chap. 2)<br>Week 3 (10/2,2,3)    Dilute Solution Thermodynamics, Molecular Weights and Sizes (Chap. 3)<br>Week 4 (10/9,9)<br>Week 5 (10/16,16,17)    Concentrated Solutions, Phase Separation Behavior, and Diffusion (Chap.4)<br>Week 6(10/23,23,24)    <br>Week 7 (10/30,30,31)    <br>Week 8 (11/6,6,7)   The Amorphous State (Chap. 5)<br>   11/7 Midterm #1 (1 hr) <br>Week 9 (11/13,13,14) <br>Week 10 (11/20,20,21)   <br>Week 11 (11/27,27,28)   The Crystalline State (Chap. 6)<br>Week 12 (12/4,4,5)   <br>Week 13 (12/11,11,12)   <br>Week 14 (12/18,18,19)   Glass-Rubber Transition Behavior (Chap. 8)<br>Week 15 (12/25,25,26) <br>    12/26 Midterm #2 (1 hr)<br>Week 16 (1/2)    <br>Week 17 (1/8,8,9)   <br>    1/15 Final (2 hrs)', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH5301701')
