CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='不勻相觸媒', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='課程內容包括基本理論、表面分析用儀器、吸附之原理與應用、酸性觸媒、金屬觸媒、觸媒與污染及工業用觸媒。//This course is intended to provide a comprehensive introduction to the preparation, characterization, and industrial applications of heterogeneous solid catalysts. Major contents of this course include the theory and application of adsorption, the instrumental analyses of solid catalyst, the preparations of various catalysts such as supported metal catalyst, acid catalyst and zeolites. The applications of solid catalyst in pollution control, petroleum processing, and other industrial practices are also introduced.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH5405701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CH'), course_name='文獻選讀 (一)', course_teacher='未  定', course_type=1, course_discription='可能的討論題材包含：<br>熱物性<br>表面、界面及奈米科學<br>光電及能源材料<br>高分子材料<br>生化及生醫工程<br>程序系統工程<br>環境工程<br>清淨技術//Possible topics include <br>thermophysical properties<br>surface, interface and nano science<br>optoelectronic and energy materials<br>polymer materials<br>biochemical and biomedical engineering<br>process systems engineering<br>environmental engineering<br>cleaner techniques', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CH5701701')
