CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='高等結構學', course_teacher='潘誠平', course_type=1, course_discription='勁度法與柔度法之矩陣結構分析，以能量原理推導分析方程式，桁架與構架之程式分析方法，結構穩定性問題之推導與解題。//(1)Basic concepts of matrix structural analysis<br>(2)The three principles of structural analysis<br>(3)Plane truss problems<br>(4)Numerical methods used for matrix structural analysis<br>(5)Space truss problems<br>(6)Plane frame problems<br>(7)Various boundary conditions<br>(8)Treatment for member loadings<br>(9)Derivations of element stiffness matrix<br>(10)Space frame problems<br>(11)Grid structures', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT5201701')
