CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='工程材料組合律', course_teacher='張大鵬', course_type=1, course_discription='簡介，張量介紹，應力與應變，彈性應力－應變關係，非線性應力－應變關係，材料破壞準則，著名組合律介紹，類值技巧及應用。//This course consists of studying the role of constitutive equation, tensor notation, kinematics of deformation, compatibility condition, finite Eulerian and Lagrangian strain tensors, infinitesimal strain tensor, force and moment equilibrium equation, stress tensor, linerar and nonlinear stress-strain relations, isotropy and anisotropy.  Application of these constitutive equations to model the behaviors of concrete and geomaterial are also addressed in the course.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT6108701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='鋼結構構件行為學', course_teacher='蕭博謙', course_type=1, course_discription='鋼結構構件之彎曲、剪力與扭力分析，結構穩定介紹，柱構件之結構行為，梁－柱構件之結構行為，梁構件之結構行為。//Elastic behavior, inelastic behavior, instability, and ultimate strength of steel structural members under bending, shear, axial force, and torsion is covered.  Instability of frames is introduced. The theory and development benind design specification are discussed.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT6301701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='結構隔減震設計', course_teacher='汪向榮', course_type=1, course_discription='介紹隔震及減震設計之基本原理，並說明及推導常用隔震支承及減震器之力學行為，進而講解隔震結構及減震結構之相關設計方法，訓練研究生對結構隔減震設計的能力。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT6305710')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='混凝土科學', course_teacher='廖敏志', course_type=1, course_discription='水泥漿體的微觀結構及性質之量測技術，水泥漿微觀結構和強度的發展，骨材的巨微觀特性及骨材混凝土界面之影響，化學摻料科學，新拌混凝土的性質與特徵，特殊混凝土，混凝土與環境之相互作用，混凝土科學研究未來展望。//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT6502701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CT'), course_name='專題研究', course_teacher='廖敏志', course_type=0, course_discription='本課程為使在職碩士專班學生具備如何進行研究的方法與概念，並協助學生探索研究主題，加強科技寫作、文字組織與溝通表達能力，將研究內容與職場工作結合。本課程內容概分為簡報技巧、研究探索、工程統計應用、研究方法及論文寫作方法。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CT9102301')
