CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='CX'), course_name='色彩工程概論', course_teacher='陳鴻興', course_type=1, course_discription='1.光學與視覺：光學原理與眼睛構造、色溫、演色性之介紹 2.色彩之描述方式：色序圖含MunSell系統、Ostwald系統、NCS系統 3.色彩之數學模式：三原色之表達方式，基色之轉換 4.CIE標準色度圖：配色函數，色度座標，RGB與XYZ轉換 5.混色 6.色彩再現原理//Let students learn colorimetry theory, color measurement, and distinguish the meanings of colorimetry and densitometry. These color science concepts are the basic tools for the application of cross-media image I/O reproduction devices.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=CX4607701')
