CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='DT'), course_name='包裝結構設計', course_teacher='許呈湧', course_type=1, course_discription='1.商品強度的認定與包裝材料的運用<br>2.物流運輸的狀況與解決方式<br>3.賣場擺設的技巧與重點.<br>4.包裝結構的設計與可靠度的要求//The course is to teach the capability of product package structure and its material. The emphasis is on the design of new structure and test of new material that enables to create a new ground of product packages.<br>1. To identify with product strength and the application of packaging material.<br>2. To study the condition of product distribution and the solution of product packaging transportation.<br>3. To realize the role of packaging in the retailed environment<br>4. To design of packaging structure according to the requirement of the validity', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=DT3508701')
