CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='DT'), course_name='材料創新運用', course_teacher='范振能', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程由設計的觀點檢視現有材料的創新應用，其範圍涵蓋工程塑膠、金屬乃至複合材料與數位建構。教學內容並包含材料特性影響產品設計的各項議題，並介紹先進材料在設計上的可能應用。學生在本課程中必須於期中撰寫研究報告並於期末執行一自行選擇之概念設計案例。藉此了解設計、材料及技術之相互關係。//This course examines various aspects of materials and techniques innovation in design, from engineering plastic and metal to composite material and digital fabrication. Course material deals with the broad issues affecting the nature of materials in architecture and product design, and provides a focused review of the state of the art materials. An additional design project and report done by the student is required to address the relationship between design, materials, and techniques.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=DT5517701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='DT'), course_name='設計研究方法', course_teacher='陳建雄', course_type=1, course_discription='介紹在設計上可採用之研究方法，其使用時機與技巧，包括質化與量化之研究方法。//Introduction to the study of basic design research methods common to industrial, interface, and interaction design.  This course will focus on both quantitative and qualitative research methodologies including the following research methods: experiment, observation, interview, and questionnaire.  Moreover, this course will emphasize that the purpose of conducting a design research study is not merely to generate a set of “good data.”  Designers need to analyze the research data and exploit the research findings in elevating the current and future designs.<br><br>The class will primarily meet in room RB-402 at 1:30-4:20pm on Thursdays.  Depending on the progress of project assignment, the class may meet at other design studios or computer labs with prior notices.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=DT5606701')
