CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='醫用超音波影像', course_teacher='沈哲州', course_type=1, course_discription='1.醫用超音波影像簡介<br>2.聲波傳遞模型<br>3.聲波的散射、衰退與斑點雜訊產生<br>4.超音波換能器<br>5.超音波陣列成像<br>6.超音波影像品質分析<br>7.都卜勒血流偵測 <br>8. 安全性與劑量//1.Overview of diagnostic ultrasonic imaging systems.<br>2.Acoustic wave propagation.<br>3.Scattering, attenuation and speckle.<br>4.Transducers - generation and detection of<br>ultrasound.<br>5.Diffraction and beam formation using arrays.<br>6.Contrast resolution.<br>7.Doppler flow detection. <br>8.Exposimetry.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5790701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='資料壓縮', course_teacher='陳建中', course_type=1, course_discription='簡介，資訊量測與熵值，霍夫曼編碼，算術編碼，機率預測模型與零值問題，詞典查詢編碼。//A. lossless Coding<br>   1. Basic information theory<br>   2. HUffman coding<br>   3. Arithmetic Coding<br>   4. Dictionary Techniques<br>B. lossy coding<br>   5. Scalar Quantization<br>   6. Vector Quantization<br>   7. Differential Encoding<br>C. Selected Topics<br>   8. Transform Coding<br>   9. Subband Coding', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5801701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='磁共振影像系統', course_teacher='黃騰毅', course_type=1, course_discription='1.簡介磁振造影系統<br>2. 磁振訊號來源 I<br>3. 磁振訊號來源 II<br>4. 影像品質<br>5. 磁振造影儀硬體設備<br>6. K空間和面迴訊影像<br>7. 假影<br>8. 快速血管攝影<br>9. 快速成像及多重線圈平行影像 <br>10. 相位對比流速影像<br>11. 擴散現象<br>12. 微灌流<br>13. 功能性磁振造影<br>14. 磁振頻譜//1.Introduction to MRI<br>2.Source of NMR signal -- I<br>3.Source of NMR signal -- II<br>4.Image quality <br>5.Hardware <br>6.K-Space and EPI<br>7.Artifact<br>8.TOF MRA<br>9.Fast scan and multi-coil parallel imaging <br>10.Phase contrast flow imaging<br>11.Diffusion<br>12.Perfusion<br>13.Functional MRI<br>14.MRS', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5831701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='數位傳輸技術', course_teacher='張立中', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在介紹現代數位通訊系統中所使用的多項傳輸技術並強調其在無線上的應用。包括離散型數據傳輸基本原則，數位調變技術，基本估計觀念和標準，線性調整式濾波演算法含最小均方和遞迴式最小平方法以及其應用和功率放大器線性化技術。研究現況實例會適時使用//This course serves as an introduction to various techniques behind modern digital communication systems, with focus being placed on wireless applications. Topics covered include fundamentals of discrete data transmission including detection, digital modulation techniques, basic concepts and criteria of estimation, linear adaptive filtering algorithms such as least mean squares and recursive least squares and their applications.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5913701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='天線', course_teacher='楊成發', course_type=1, course_discription='1.天線導論 2.天線陣列 3.線狀與面狀天線、寬頻天線、孔狀天線 4.天線合成技術 5.天線系統與測量方法 6.電磁數值方法應用於天線之設計//1. To introduce the fundamental principles of antenna theory.<br>2. To apply them to the analysis, design, and measurements of antennas.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5914701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='微波元件設計', course_teacher='馬自莊', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程首先介紹微波網路分析理論，並以此為基礎深入探討微波元件之設計原理及實際應用。被動元件方面，將依序介紹微波共振器、集總元件、微波濾波器理論，以及近年新研發之傳輸線結構。主動元件部分，將先介紹系統雜音分析，復探討微波放大器之匹配、低雜音、寬頻及高功率設計，最後介紹混波器與震盪器之設計原理。//Transmission Lines.<br>Coupled Line Theory.<br>Directional coupler.<br>Filter basics.<br>Coupled-line filters.<br>Microwave Amplifier Design.<br>Low Noise Amplifier.<br>Power Amplifier.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE5915701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='電力系統控制與運轉(一)', course_teacher='張宏展', course_type=1, course_discription='發電機組特性，火力電廠之經濟運轉及其解法，傳輸損耗，機組運轉之認定，能源限制下之發電，火力與火力發電之協調，燃料預算與規劃所用到的能源生產成本模型，發電控制，購電成本評估，電力系統安全性評估。//1.  Characteristics of Power Generation Units (2)<br>2. Economic Dispatch of Thermal Units and Methods of Solution (6)<br>3.    Transmission Losses (6)<br>4.   Unit Commitment (3)<br>5.   Generation with Limited Energy Supply (3)<br>6. Hydrothermal Coordination (3)<br>7. Energy Production Cost Models for Fuel Budgeting and Planning (3)<br>8. Control of Generation (3)<br>9. Interchange Evaluation and Power Pools (3)<br>10.   Power System Security (3)<br>11. State estimation in Power Systems (3)', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE6201701')
