CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EE'), course_name='排隊理論', course_teacher='鍾順平', course_type=1, course_discription='條件機率及期望值，馬可夫鏈，指數型分布及波以松程序，連續時間馬可夫鏈，更新程序，生死佇列，馬可夫佇列，G/M/1，G/M/m，佇列網路。//1. Introduction<br>  ‧ Characteristics of Queueing Processes<br>  ‧ Poisson Process and Exponential Distribution<br>  ‧ Markovian Property<br>  ‧ Markov Chains <br>2. Simple Markovian Queueing Models<br>  ‧ Birth-Death Processes<br>  ‧ Steady-State Solution<br>  ‧ A/B/C/D/E<br>3. Advanced Markovian Models<br>  ‧ Bulk Arrivals and Services<br>  ‧ Erlang Arrivals and Services  <br>  ‧ Priority Queues<br>4. Queueing Networks<br>  ‧ Series Queues<br>  ‧ Jackson Networks<br>  ‧ Cyclic Queues<br>5. Models with General Arrivals or Service Patterns<br>  ‧ General Arrivals<br>  ‧ General Services', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EE6600701')
