CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EP'), course_name='職業教育與訓練', course_teacher='詹雅晴', course_type=0, course_discription='為符合技術及職業教育法第24條第1項之規定，讓同學正確認識技職教育，培養正確職業觀念俾使日後於教育現場能協助學生選擇合適之升學進路', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EP4820301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='EP'), course_name='教育社會學', course_teacher='翁楊絲茜', course_type=0, course_discription='介紹教育社會學的意義、範圍、教育社會學的理論等。//The purpose of this course is to do a comprehensive examination of educational institutions that will familiarize students with the main findings, theoretical perspectives and research methods employed in the sociological study of education. Topics include the purpose and functions of education; educational stratification; socioeconomic, gender, and racial inequalities in education; curriculum development and reform; and schooling and the labor market. The course also examines alternative forms of schooling; the influence of peer cultures and school climate; and the institutional challenges associated with school violence. Upon completion of the course, students will understand and know the changes in educational practices, the major debates in educational research and policy, and the key educational issues and relevant sociological concepts.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=EP5509301')
