CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='ET'), course_name='工程數學(一)', course_teacher='王蒼容', course_type=0, course_discription='The aim of this course is to help the students build up the fundamentals for solving the differential equations. After learning these skills, the students can apply these skills to help solve the differential equations encountered in the Physics, Chemistry, and any other associated courses. In this course, first, we will start with the first-order differential equations and then continue with the second-order differential equations. Also, we will also apply the Laplace Transform to transform the differential equations to linear algebraic equations, which can be solved easily by simple manipulation. Furthermore, series solutions are introduced to help solve advanced differential equations. Without loss of generality, numerical approximation is proposed to train the students solve the differential equations by using the computer. We hope the students can learn the skills and enjoy the process when they take this course.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=ET3001303')
