CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='ET'), course_name='多媒體無線網路', course_teacher='鄭瑞光', course_type=1, course_discription='(1)Multimedia Applications (2)QoS Fundamentals (3)QoS Mechanisms (4)Selected Standards This course will give an overview of the multimedia application. The fundamentals of Quality of Service (QoS)is then introduced. Some commonly used QoS Mechanisms will be given. Finally, we will use some popular wireless standards as examples to illustrate the usage of the QoS mechanisms.<br>本課程旨在提供多媒體無線網路相關的基礎，從架構、應用，以及實際無線網路相關規格等不同角度，說明服務品質(QoS)的相關問題及解決方案，並以目前常用的無線網路標準為例，介紹實際的解決方案。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=ET5907701')
