CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='ET'), course_name='雙極互補金氧半混合訊號積體電路', course_teacher='張勝良', course_type=1, course_discription='第一章：深次微米金氧半及異質接面電晶體元件物理：Deep submicron CMOS and SiGe HBT device physics and models. 第二章：雙極性互補式金氧半電晶體製程技術：SiGe BiCMOS front-end and back-end fabrication processing. 第三章：高速高密低電壓數位與高頻類比次電路：Adder, counter, memory, and microcontroller. BiCMOS amplifier and current mirror, and BiCMOS circuit layout. 第四章：電磁相容性設計：Substrate coupling, ESD, EFT, system design for EMC. 第五章：混合數位與類比電路：custom analog and digital filter design, delta-sigma data converter fundamentals, fractional-n PLL. 第六章：混合訊號電路設計分析與實習：Design、simulation and measurement of a mixed-signal circuit project.//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=ET6008701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='ET'), course_name='金氧半元件', course_teacher='林保宏', course_type=1, course_discription='直流電流電壓特性、短與窄通道效應、熱載子與元件退化、元件的交流特性、雙極－金氧半電路//1.Process and Device models in microelectronics<br>2.Fundamentals of Device Physics, Design, Simulations and Simulation Tools<br>3.MOS Physics and MOS Capacitors<br>4.Long- Channel MOSEFETs<br>5.Submicron MOSEFETs<br>6.Isolation Structures<br>7.Gate Technology<br>8.Hot Carrier Effects', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=ET6306701')
