CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='財務管理', course_teacher='張光第', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程以探討公司之財務政策與金融系統（市場、機構、工具）為主，舉凡資金成本，資本預算、金錢之時間價值均為主要中心。此外，風險報酬分析、資本結構、股利政策、短期與長期資金之籌措與應用，及各種籌措資金工具和普通股，優先股與可轉換公司債皆為研討範圍。而資本市場之利率時間結構與效率問題，亦為本課程之重點。//Financial Management, or say Corporate Finance, is a fundamental course to bring students into the world of finance. It focuses on how companies invest and how they raise the money to pay for these investments. In this course, the basic principles of financial management and how to apply them will be covered. In addition, different source of finance for companies will also be discussed. It is my hope to initial your interest about finance and to build a solid foundation for studying more advanced courses.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB2000701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='創業與財務', course_teacher='林建成', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程目標在提供創業之財務規劃及投資考量所需之相關知識，並幫助同學建立完整的分析架構，歸納出各種解決方案，以符合新創事業的需求。同時，本課程也將針對公司生命週期之不同階段，提出符合公司需求之財務策略。此外，亦希望能夠奠定同學堅實的財務管理基礎，並學習如何撰寫創業籌資報告。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB2103701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='期貨與選擇權', course_teacher='繆維中', course_type=1, course_discription='The major goal of this course is to provide students with complete understanding of many modern financial products and their markets. Topics such as forward and futures, swaps, and options will be fully covered. Furthermore, the basic pricing methods of these innovative products will be emphasized in this course. Finally, although this is a course originally for students in Department of Finance, I think the knowledge mentioned in this course is necessary even for a student who majors in Business.//The major goal of this course is to provide students with complete understanding of many modern financial products and their markets. It also provides an introductory concept for students of how different frameworks and analytical tool can be used to manage the varied challenges faced by managers in different derivatives markets.  Topics such as forward and futures, swaps, and options will be fully covered. Furthermore, the basic pricing methods of these innovative products will be emphasized in this course. Finally, although this is a course originally for students in Department of Finance, I think the knowledge mentioned in this course is necessary even for a student who majors in Business.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB2300701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='基礎理財規劃實務', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='建立正確基本理財觀念，學習規劃個人財務收支，善用一般金融工具，在風險考量下做最有效的運用，藉由適宜的投資方式，逐步達成人生財富目標。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB3602701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='貨幣銀行學', course_teacher='林清珮(待)', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程主要提供學生貨幣和銀行的基本概念，包括貨幣的功能、貨幣供給量、中央銀行貨幣政策、銀行做為金融中介所扮演的角色、商業銀行的創新發展、利率的決定和風險結構與期間結構等，外加貨幣需求理論以及貨幣與通貨膨脹的關聯性，另外，外匯市場、國際收支等國際金融市場的理論與實務亦涵蓋在內。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB3604701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='基金管理', course_teacher='曾凱逸', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在建立學生投資組合管理知識，藉由系統化的知識教授及諸多的基金管理實例輔助，以使學生能對投資組合的學術理論及實務運作有深入了解。課程中探究報酬和風險的關係、投資組合分散及效率市場理論等重要的投資學理論，並對實務上的分析方法、基金管理流程及策略、和基金型態均深入說明，以使學生透過課程的學習，達到深化投資領域的知識。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FB3608701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FB'), course_name='品牌價值創新講座', course_teacher='張志賢', course_type=0, course_discription='1.探討品牌行銷與企業財務績效的關係<br>2.借鏡成功品牌資產創新範例培養同學未來出社會的競爭優勢', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FBG006301')
