CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='實用華語班(第三級)', course_teacher='陳方玓', course_type=1, course_discription='此課程為中階華語課程，除了日常生活之華語、認字及文法外，學生能學到更多文化層面之華語，如:校園生活用語，文化差異等主題。<br>修完此課後，學生將能了解較長的對話，也能讀短篇文章，也能用口語或書寫表達自己意見。<br><br>詳細課程如下: <br>1. 新室友 2. 吃什麼好 3. 我想去臺灣 4. 談談地理吧 5. 氣候跟出差 6. 考不完的試 7. 念大學真不容易//Practical Audio-Visual Chinese 2nd Edition, Book 2, Unit 1 –7<br>about disease, question words as indefinites, tense<br>about traveling, ask for directions<br>in a restaurant and manners, Chinese food<br>conversation on the phone, verbal suffix 過 to show experience<br>similarity and disparity, comparison<br>directional compounds<br>把 as disposal construction', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1043701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='實用華語班(第四級)', course_teacher='陳方玓', course_type=1, course_discription='此課程為高階華語課程，學生能學到更多文化層面之華語，如:科學、歷史、地理文化等相關主題。<br>修完此課後，學生將能了解短篇演講、撰寫短篇文章，也能快速閱讀簡單文章。<br><br>詳細課程如下: <br>1. 中國新年晚會 2. 我們的休閒活動 3. 你看不看電視 4. 這個電影真好看 5. 我愛看表演 6. 小心壞習慣//This course focuses on everyday Chinese.<br>Through the course, Students will learn about characters &vocabulary words and phrases & typical and situational sentence patterns.<br>Students will be able to speak more complicated sentences fluently and to use with no difficulties.<br><br>*Oral and aural proficiency <br>*Foundational grammar for complicated sentences <br>*Character recognition<br>*Chinese dictionary use', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1044701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='實用華語班(第五級)', course_teacher='李蘭儀', course_type=1, course_discription='此課程為高階華語課程，學生能學到更多文化層面之華語，如:戲劇、風俗文化、文學、環境等相關主題，學生將學習較複雜的句型等。<br>修完此課後，學生將能用流利且正確之中文與人溝通，並能了解大部份之演講內容、撰寫文章，也能閱讀報紙新聞<br><br>詳細課程如下: <br>1. 因小失大 2. 春節 3. 活到老學到老 4. 不經一事不長一智 5. 世界運動會 6. 休閒活動的新趨勢//The topics discussed in class include campus life, everyday life and differences.<br>Through the course, students will learn about characters &vocabulary and phrases &typical and situational sentence patterns.<br>Students will be able to express themselves in Chinese (both speaking and writing) more accurately. Understand longer conversation and read short articles.<br><br>*Chinese conversation <br>*Basic vocabulary and reading<br>*Character writing  <br>*Culture learning', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1045701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階華語班(第一級)', course_teacher='李蘭儀', course_type=1, course_discription='一、課程以華語生活化溝通為主題，以最基礎之華文日常生活溝通為主要授課內容，包含食、衣、住、行等基本生活會話。<br>二、以新版初階「實用視聽華語」為主要教材，除訓練學員日常華語聽說溝通之能力，亦訓練其認字及簡易華語書寫能力。<br>三、配合課本主題，介紹學生中華文化及相關活動，以加深其對中華文化之了解。<br>四、配合課本各主題之句型進行句子代換練習、造句練習等，亦加強簡易中文字書寫能力。//This course is designed for international students who learn Mandarin as the second language and have had intermediate level understanding and skills in listening, speaking, reading and writing. This course is .based on the textbook of Practical Audio-Visual Chinese Vol. 3, plus relevant materials and supplementary handouts, which will provide students with more advanced vocabularies and written expressions so they can better perform in reading, listening, speaking and writing. More specific issues and topics will be introduced to students for further discussions and exchanging ideas for mutual understanding and sharpen their communicative skills. Moreover, students will be trained to practice writing articles to be able to fully express their thoughts in a more systematic manner.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1051701')
