CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='初級英文寫作(一)', course_teacher='黃敏裕', course_type=1, course_discription='This writing course aims to help students write unified paragraphs. It takes students from paragrpah structuring to essay writing through a process approach. Students will be able to generate ideas and organize them on paper, create various paragraph types, and order paragraphs into cohesive and coherent essays. Grammar will be addressed as well. The class will be conducted as lectures and pair/group/class discussion. For writing assignments, pair and individul tasks will be given. The course materials include one required textbook and several handouts.//This writing course aims to help students write unified paragraphs. It takes students from paragrpah structuring to essay writing through a process approach. Students will be able to generate ideas and organize them on paper, create various paragraph types, and order paragraphs into cohesive and coherent essays. Grammar will be addressed as well. The class will be conducted as lectures and pair/group/class discussion. For writing assignments, pair and individul tasks will be given. The course materials include one required textbook and several handouts.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1231701')
