CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階英文閱讀', course_teacher='陳佩瑩', course_type=1, course_discription='This course aims to increase students’ accuracy of reading comprehension, extend knowledge, enlarge vocabulary, consolidate reading skills, and generate critical thinking ability so as to help students elevate their reading proficiency level. Text reading, analyzing, answering questions orally or writing on the worksheets are centered through group or class discussions in class. To boost learners’ reading confidence and enhance their ability to better appreciate the power and beauty of the target language, students are required not only to read the selected textbook readings but a novel in the original, which group discussions, collaborative learning, themes exploring, and presentations of sharing the learning outcomes are emphasized and incorporated with personal reading and writing. Ultimately, students are encouraged to take the initiative to read or search for more information related to their interests to expand and deepen their reading experiences.<br>本課程將透過各種不同閱讀文體題材，如各類小說、文學作品、短篇文章及報章新聞，提升閱讀理解力、增加字彙量，及增進其書寫與口說英語的技能，並積極參與課堂小組討論。學生需在課前完成所規定閱讀的文章內容，於課堂小組討論時間，提出自己對於文章的批判思考，並同時說明相關指定詞彙之定義，及課後皆須撰寫當週討論之相關閱讀心得，期許學生藉由系列的英語及思考訓練，能展現具有成熟批判性思維的反思和論點。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1921701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階英文閱讀', course_teacher='蘇琬婷', course_type=1, course_discription='This course aims to increase students’ accuracy of reading comprehension, extend knowledge, enlarge vocabulary, consolidate reading skills, and generate critical thinking ability so as to help students elevate their reading proficiency level. Text reading, analyzing, answering questions orally or writing on the worksheets are centered through group or class discussions in class. To boost learners’ reading confidence and enhance their ability to better appreciate the power and beauty of the target language, students are required not only to read the selected textbook readings but a novel in the original, which group discussions, collaborative learning, themes exploring, and presentations of sharing the learning outcomes are emphasized and incorporated with personal reading and writing. Ultimately, students are encouraged to take the initiative to read or search for more information related to their interests to expand and deepen their reading experiences.<br>本課程將透過各種不同閱讀文體題材，如各類小說、文學作品、短篇文章及報章新聞，提升閱讀理解力、增加字彙量，及增進其書寫與口說英語的技能，並積極參與課堂小組討論。學生需在課前完成所規定閱讀的文章內容，於課堂小組討論時間，提出自己對於文章的批判思考，並同時說明相關指定詞彙之定義，及課後皆須撰寫當週討論之相關閱讀心得，期許學生藉由系列的英語及思考訓練，能展現具有成熟批判性思維的反思和論點。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1921702')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階英語溝通', course_teacher='周雅芬', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在增進學生英語口頭溝通技巧能力，不僅教導學生用正確的發音語調及語句與英美人士作日常一般性的交談，除了口語的流利性，更著重培養用詞的精確性，溝通前的準備、組織技巧，善用傾聽技巧，使能在專業領域上適切地以英文表達，有效溝通。<br>This course is conducted with an emphasis on social interaction and cooperative dialogue. It serves to teach students to adopt a flexible range of listening strategies and give them a platform to safely practice their production of English conversation for professional purposes.  Each individual brings unique background knowledge to their learning and along with it unique requirements for their further advancement. This course strives to personalize content; each student will be able to apply their own experiences and abilities to best advance their English language learning specifically in their field of study to prepare them for professional life.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1931701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階英語溝通', course_teacher='周雅芬', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在增進學生英語口頭溝通技巧能力，不僅教導學生用正確的發音語調及語句與英美人士作日常一般性的交談，除了口語的流利性，更著重培養用詞的精確性，溝通前的準備、組織技巧，善用傾聽技巧，使能在專業領域上適切地以英文表達，有效溝通。<br>This course is conducted with an emphasis on social interaction and cooperative dialogue. It serves to teach students to adopt a flexible range of listening strategies and give them a platform to safely practice their production of English conversation for professional purposes.  Each individual brings unique background knowledge to their learning and along with it unique requirements for their further advancement. This course strives to personalize content; each student will be able to apply their own experiences and abilities to best advance their English language learning specifically in their field of study to prepare them for professional life.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1931702')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FE'), course_name='進階英語溝通', course_teacher='David P', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在增進學生英語口頭溝通技巧能力，不僅教導學生用正確的發音語調及語句與英美人士作日常一般性的交談，除了口語的流利性，更著重培養用詞的精確性，溝通前的準備、組織技巧，善用傾聽技巧，使能在專業領域上適切地以英文表達，有效溝通。<br>This course is conducted with an emphasis on social interaction and cooperative dialogue. It serves to teach students to adopt a flexible range of listening strategies and give them a platform to safely practice their production of English conversation for professional purposes.  Each individual brings unique background knowledge to their learning and along with it unique requirements for their further advancement. This course strives to personalize content; each student will be able to apply their own experiences and abilities to best advance their English language learning specifically in their field of study to prepare them for professional life.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FE1931703')
