CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='商用英文', course_teacher='林澄億', course_type=1, course_discription='The goal of this course is to teach students the English they will need to communicate effectively in a business environment. They learn key vocabulary, social language, and structures through a progression of models and practice activities, helping to integrate their L-S-R-W skills. Realistic tasks provide opportunities for students to produce the language they will need in common business situations. With an introduction and a practice test of the Test of English for International Communication (New TOEIC plus Writing and Speaking tests), the course also serves to familiarize students with the format, directions, difficulty level and substance of this important work place certification so as to indicate their general strengths and weakness in English before actually taking it.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL1008701')
