CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='中譯英', course_teacher='賈繼中', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程希望讓學生透過閱讀各個不同領域的文章，能喚起對語言的敏感度、鋒利思想，再配合老師的講解，針對各類文章選取部分斷段落做中翻英的實際演練。從習作中間感受中英雙語的差異，提升措詞表達能力。透過腦力激盪，大家集思廣義，仔細推敲整理出更多面向、更貼切的譯法。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL3514701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='英語辯論', course_teacher='卜莎娜', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程將訓練學生高階英語口語技巧，演辯討論及發表實務。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL3515701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='英語句法學', course_teacher='陳献忠', course_type=1, course_discription='This course aims to study the sentence structure or grammar of the English language. Although different theories such as Generative Grammar, Categorical Grammar, Dependency Grammar and Functionalist Grammar will be introduced as different approaches on which the study of English sentence structure can be based, the majority of class hours will be used to demonstrate how Generative Grammar can be used to analyze sentences, especially the Government and Binding theory and the Principles and Parameters framework. In this class, syntax will be regarded as the study of language specifics in English and as an important tool to start any linguistic analysis. To emphasize the practical or functional aspect of the syntactic structure, language parsing as well as a simple contrastive study between English and Chinese will be briefly covered.     <br>英語句法學旨在使用不同語法理論研究英語的句子結構，本課程主要採用的語法理論有二：杭士基的生成語法與陳氏情境語法。本課程除了理論的介紹之外，格外重視句法的應用價值，譬如語言剖析，比較語言研究，以及語言分析。有鑒於句法與語意的唇齒關係，本課程也特別介紹句法學與語意學的介面概念，指出句法學與語意學的分工合作，前者研究語言特異性，後者研究語言的共通性。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL3624701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='初級西班牙文(一)', course_teacher='馮志宇', course_type=1, course_discription='教學內容著重於西班牙文之生活語文能力訓練，採多元方式教學並搭配影音教材輔助學生基礎聽、說、讀、寫能力。1.西班牙語文發音 2.日常生活會話、簡易問答 3.閱讀日常生活中的標示(廣告、餐廳菜單) 4.字彙組織及句型基本結構 5.西語國家文化簡述//★Goal: <br>The aim of this course is to build up students’ basic daily life terminology and the rules of pronunciation.  Regular vocabulary practices are given to strengthen their consciousness. Proper application of pronunciation is to enhance their verbal skill.  To help students overcome the fear of facing second language is the aim as well.<br>★Content: <br>This course explores basic Spanish pronunciation and vocabulary.  Audio-visual teaching materials will be used to help and strengthen students’ basic listening and speaking skills of pronunciation and vocabulary by practicing them clearly and regularly.<br>★Outcomes: <br>Students will learn how to identify basic Spanish pronunciation and vocabulary.  They will be able to absorb the basic verbal skills and apply the knowledge to produce correct and clear outcomes. And they will get used to the basic sense of Spanish verbal skills.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL3798701')
