CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='外語學習焦慮', course_teacher='曾文鐽', course_type=1, course_discription='This course aims to provide a critical and conceptually thorough understanding of foreign language learning anxiety. Language anxiety hallmarks an important research enterprise in second language acquisition, and its significance has been well-recognized by researchers. This is a three-hour credit graduate course that introduces and discusses related theories, studies, and methodologies in relation to language anxiety. The course will also review various yet inter-related concepts of language anxiety such as personality, motivation, and willingness to communicate. In particular, the typical instruments designed for measuring language anxiety will be likewise introduced and discussed in the course.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL5261701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FL'), course_name='資訊科技融入教學', course_teacher='陳秀玲', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程旨在探討資訊科技融入教學的理論與實務，期能藉由重要文獻導讀、課堂討論、探討與評估不同資訊科技在教學上的運用等方式，幫助學生奠定資訊科技融入教學的基礎，並能應用到未來的教學。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FL5407701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='專題研討(一)', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=0, course_discription='經由產、官、學、研各界人士到系演講，針對學術專題研究成果進行研討，並就管理技術、發展趨勢以及成功個案等介紹不同行業的營運方式及競爭力分析。//The seminar will be given by the invited speakers from scholars and experts of finance field in the industries, universities, government and research institutes. The topics include the following: 1.Banking(consumer loans, business loans, wealth management) 2.Insurance 3.Securities and Futures 4.Investment consulting firms 5.Corporate Finance 6.Venture Capital', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5001301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='專題研討(三)', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=0, course_discription='//The seminar will be given by the invited speakers from scholars and experts of finance field in the industries, universities, government and research institutes. The topics include the following: 1.Banking(consumer loans, business loans, wealth management) 2.Insurance 3.Securities and Futures 4.Investment consulting firms 5.Corporate Finance 6.Venture Capital', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5003301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='博彩管制與產業分析', course_teacher='劉代洋', course_type=1, course_discription='1.前言:遊戲與博彩、博彩在台灣、博彩的正反意見、博彩玩家檔案。<br>2.博彩與公共政策議題：合法化與管制。<br>3.世界各國賭博合法化之趨勢:各國合法化背景與原因,市場結構與管制作法。<br>4.美國博彩產業合法化與發展趨勢:大西洋城,內華達州拉斯維加斯市。<br>5.美國以外世界各國:澳門,新加坡,台灣,英國,芬蘭,韓國,馬來西亞,澳大利亞。<br>6.博彩產業發展和生活經濟。<br>7.博彩產業發展社會成本分析(青少年問題,組織犯罪,貪污,家庭失和等)。<br>8.問題賭博和病態賭博。<br>9.法律管制與限制:許可執照,地點,信用,遊戲玩法。<br>10.美國內華達州博彩法律管制(PART Ⅰ)。<br>11.美國內華達州遊戲機(gaming devices and slot machines)，法律管制PART Ⅱ-Regulation 14。<br>12.歐洲各國博彩法律管制及遊戲機管制規定(英國,芬蘭,義大利等)。<br>13.亞太各國博彩法律管制及遊戲機管制規定(澳門,韓國,馬來西亞,澳大利亞等)。//1.Introduction: gaming and gambling, gaming in Taiwan <br>2.Gaming and public policy: legalization and regulation<br>3.The trend in world gaming industry <br>4. The trend and development of commercial gaming in USA<br>5. The trend and development of commercial gaming in other Major countries<br>6. Gaming industry and economic development<br>7. Social cost in commercial gaming<br>8. Problem gambling and Pathological gambling<br>9. Rules and regulations in commercial gaming<br>10  Rules and regulations in commercial gaming in Nevada<br>11. Rules and regulations in gaming devices and slot machines-regulation 14<br>12. Rules and regulations in commercial gaming in Europe<br>13. Rules and regulations in commercial gaming in Asia-Pacific region', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5103701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='財報分析', course_teacher='陳俊男', course_type=1, course_discription='This course is designed to combines accounting, finance and business strategy theory with real accounting information to help students learn how to use financial statement data in analysis, forecast and valuation. A prerequisite of introductory accounting and introductory finance courses is recommended before taking this course. It will discuss more traditional financial statement analysis topics such as business analysis, accounting analysis, and financial statement analysis. Particularly, it covers all of the commonly used valuation models; i.e., an unusually rigorous treatment of valuation with multiples as well as five models derived from basic discounted cash flow theory (the dividend discount model, the flow to equity model, the free cash flow model, the adjusted present value model, and the residual income model). The result of the analysis can be used to make various decisions.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5201701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='線性模式', course_teacher='張琬喻', course_type=1, course_discription='//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5301701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='財務管理', course_teacher='張光第', course_type=1, course_discription='財務管理為財務金融專業之基礎課程之一，故為管理學院學生必要修習之課程。<br>本課程屬概論課程，目的在使學生對財務管理有一全盤性的了解。本課程內容包括財務比率分析、現金管理、資本預算(投資)決策、融資決策與負債管理、資本結構與股利政策、衍生性商品與風險管理、實質選擇權與財務規劃、合併與收購決策等介紹。本課程結合哈佛個案，以強化課程內容，使理論更貼近實務。課程綱要依照哈佛個案及上述內容分為五大模組，以掌握財務管理的關鍵因素。//Financial Management, or Corporate Finance, is a fundamental course to bring students into the world of Finance. It focuses on how companies invest and how they raise the money to pay for these investments. This course will cover the topics of the analysis of financial ratios, cash flow management, capital budgeting, financing dedicions and liability management, captial structrue and divident policy, real option and financial planning, and mergers and acquisions. Harvard cases will be covered to enhance the applicable essence of theroies learned from Finance textbooks in class to the real world.  The course is designed to categorize the subjects outlined above into five Modules based on Harvard cases in order to capture the core factors of Fiancial Management.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5401701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='投資學', course_teacher='陳俊男', course_type=1, course_discription='//過去全球資本市場因金融海嘯而慘遭重創，近年來景氣回溫卻大幅波動，為使學生掌握當前投資環境的變化，課程強調理論和實務搭配教學，期望透過此課程來提供學生投資新視野。The main objective of this course is to acquaint students with the selection of common stocks, bonds, and other securities from the perspectives of both the individual and institutional investor.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5501701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='投資銀行與併購', course_teacher='謝劍平', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程乃針對管理學院碩士班學生，有志學習投資銀行及併購者，提供投資銀行及金控各類相關業務之分析架構，並深度剖析探討併購相關趨勢及流程，且著重實務面之探討，將不定期邀集實務界相關人士蒞臨演講。課程中強調互動學習，課前必須對財經相關資訊或問題有所準備，並在課堂中踴躍發問。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5506701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='投資銀行與併購', course_teacher='謝劍平', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程乃針對管理學院碩士班學生，有志學習投資銀行及併購者，提供投資銀行及金控各類相關業務之分析架構，並深度剖析探討併購相關趨勢及流程，且著重實務面之探討，將不定期邀集實務界相關人士蒞臨演講。課程中強調互動學習，課前必須對財經相關資訊或問題有所準備，並在課堂中踴躍發問。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5506702')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='隨機過程與財務應用', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='機率論復習<br>波松過程<br>離散時間馬可夫鏈<br>連續時間馬可夫鏈<br>布朗運動及平賭過程<br>隨機微積分及伊藤引理<br>幾何布朗運動<br>隨機微分方程<br>離散時間模型之套利定價理論//Review of probability theory<br>Poisson processes<br>Discrete-time Markov chains<br>Continuous-time Markov chains<br>Brownian motions and martingales<br>Stochastic calculus and Ito’s lemma<br>Geometric Brownian motions<br>Stochastic differential equations<br>Arbitrage pricing in discrete-time models', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN5805701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='FN'), course_name='財務理論', course_teacher='陳俊男', course_type=1, course_discription='//The course will give PhD students an overview of the core of finance. It will cover some important financial theories about asset allocation and asset pricing, including CAPM, APT, MM theorem, Black-Scholes-Merton option pricing formula, etc. Moreover, the modern consumption-based asset pricing model will be mentioned in the course, and if the time is enough, some concepts about Behavioral Finance will be touched, too.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=FN6401701')
