CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='GE'), course_name='政黨政治與民主發展', course_teacher='劉公昭', course_type=0, course_discription='一、政黨的意義、起源與發展。二、政黨制度形成之因事、類型及現代化的關係。三、政黨組織的性質與法律規範、類型、結構、發展的趨勢，政黨的現代化與民主發展。四、政黨與選舉的關係(1)理論模型(2)政黨在選舉中之角色(3)政黨提名制度、輔選之角色變遷(4)美國初選制之利弊得失。五、政黨與政府的關係(英、美、中)。六、政黨之重組、衰退、反對黨之挑戰及文化多元主義與國家整合(政黨政治的變遷與民主的挑戰)。七、結論及建議。//', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=GE3402301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='GE'), course_name='社會科學概論', course_teacher='陳淵源', course_type=0, course_discription='//An Introduction to the social science is to discuss the relationship between human and human, human and circumstance, and human and himself. At first, this course lets the students understand the development of the social science, the thought network of the social science, and learn the methodology of social science to analyze the social phenomena, and to discuss social problems. The second, this course is to introduce briefly sociology, political science, economics, law, anthropology, and psychology. At last, this course provides a space to discuss the relationship between social science and modern world, and social science and globalization. Let students understand the whole social science, to promote the progress and development of human society.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=GE3405301')
