CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='GE'), course_name='消費者保護法', course_teacher='林瑞珠', course_type=0, course_discription='隨著現代商業社會之發展，社會大眾日益仰賴經濟實力與專業知識居優勢地位之企業組織供給日常生活所需之商品或服務，規範消費法律關係之消費者保護法及其相關法規應運而生，已成為與民眾日常生活息息相關之重要法規。是以，本課程將以消費者保護法、消費者保護法施行細則及其他相關法規為重心，藉由教師解說、演講分享與分組討論，使學生熟悉法律上關於消費關係之規範，並藉由課程活動，以對話式案例教學型態，協助學生在案例情境中學習運用法律處理生活中的消費爭議。<br><br>With the development of modern commercial society, the public is increasingly dependent on the organization with the economic strength and expertise supplying the goods or services required for daily life. Consumer Protection Law is meant to govern the consumer legal relations by large. So far, related rules and/or derivative legislations have been complemented to cover most of the consumer affairs of people’s daily lives. This course will cover the context of Consumer Protection Law, Consumer Protection Law Enforcement Rules and other relevant laws and regulations. With the teacher’s commentary, lectures and group discussions, students shall get familiar with the laws and regulations concerning consumer relations. In additions, during curricular activities and conversational case study, students will learn to deal with daily consumer disputes by using laws.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=GE3725301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='GE'), course_name='人際關係', course_teacher='林慧慈', course_type=0, course_discription='介紹人際關係與溝通的相關心理學知識，並針對常見的溝通困境進行溝通技巧演練。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=GE3726301')
