CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='統計學(一)', course_teacher='葉瑞徽', course_type=0, course_discription='This course is designed to help students understand the basic statistical concepts and analyses for facilitating management decisions. You will also learn to think critically about how statistics is used by others and how it impacts your day to day life. 這門課的目的在學習如何使用統計學的基本概念與分析的方法來幫助我們解決管理決策上的問題，然而，我們的終極目標並不在於習得這個工具、知道在不同時機套用不同的公式或者為未來的研究所之路奠下良好的基礎（雖然那也是研習本課程的收穫），我們的目標在於透過彼此之間的激勵發展深度的學習，並進而對我們的思想、行為產生持續性的影響。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM3003302')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='管理數學', course_teacher='李強笙', course_type=0, course_discription='課程主要目的是為數學規劃，實驗計劃，及預測學等學科奠定數學基礎。課程介紹矩陣及高斯消去法，向量空間，網路之矩陣，線性轉換，正交法，最小平方近似值，快速傅力葉轉換，行列式，艾根值及艾根向量，及其它相關課題。//The goal of Managerial Mathematics is to provide a solid mathematical foundation of mathematical modeling, programming, design of experiment, and prediction sciences. This course mainly covers subjects of Linear Algebra to present the major concepts of linear algebra clearly and give students basic understanding of its application. In this course, we will learn the basic concepts of matrix algebra such as linear equations, matrices, determinants, vector spaces, inner product spaces, linear transformations, eigenvalues, and eigenvectors. The matlab or mathematical software for computing matrix will be introduced.<br>‧Linear Equations <br>‧Matrices<br>‧Determinants<br>‧Vector Spaces<br>‧Inner Product Spaces<br>‧Linear Transformations<br>‧Eigenvalues, and Eigenvectors', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM3005301')
