CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='工作研究實習', course_teacher='紀佳芬', course_type=0, course_discription='介紹動作與時間研究之基本觀念與實施步驟；對方法研究與時間衡量常用之技術說明其理論基礎；了解最新的工作研究技術；配合上課進度示範，實習，並分組作專題研究。//Through in-lab exercises, group project discussions and on-site practices, students get to practice the appropriate use of work methods and measurement techniques, exercise process analysis tools and operation analysis tools of a given work, learn the correct procedures to establish a time standard through the use of time study, work sampling, predetermined time system, and standard data system. The incentive plans and lean production are integrated in the practice as well in order to improve productivity within the total production management structure in an organization.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM4703301')
