CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='服務管理', course_teacher='郭人介', course_type=1, course_discription='其主要是建立系統化的服務系統設計與服務作業管理方式，其內容包括服務本質的瞭解、服務設計、服務系統規劃、服務地點選擇、服務場所佈置、服務程序設計、服務自動化及電腦化、服務作業管理人員管理、儀器設備管理、服務存貨管理、服務等候線管理及服務績效管理等。//This course mainly introduces the development, design and management of service systems. The contents include introduction of service industry, service design, service systems planning, site selection, layout, service process design, service automation, service process management, facility management, inventory control, queuing, and performance management.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM5711701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='供應鏈管理', course_teacher='周碩彥', course_type=1, course_discription='(1)Introduction to Supply Chain Management (2)Logistics Netowork Configuration (3)Inventory Management and Risk Pooling (4)The Value of Information (5)Supply Chain Integration (6)Strategic Alliances (7)Procurement and Outsourcing Strategies (8)International Issues in Supply Chain Management (9)Coordinated Product and Supply Chain Design (10)Customer Value and Supply Chain  Management (11)Information Technology for Supply Chain Management (12)Decision Support Systems for Supply Chain Management//Exploring fundamental and emerging topics in global supply chain management, including inventory management, network planning, information visibility, supply contract, integration, alliances, procurement, product design, global logistics, risk management, pricing, IT and standards. Contents will be suitable for students pursuing research and/or professional career in this discipline. In addition to the text, simulation games, cases will also be used for presentation and discussion.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM5802701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='資料探勘應用', course_teacher='郭人介', course_type=1, course_discription='(1)Introduction to Data Mining (2)Data Warehouse and OLAP Technology (3)Data Processing (4)Data Mining Primitives, Languages, and System Architectures (5)Concept Description:Characterization and Comparison (6)Mining Association Rules in Large Databases (7)Classification and Prediction (8)Cluster Analysis (9)Mining Complex Types of Data (10)Applications and Trends in Data Mining (11)Biomedical and DNA Data Analysis (12)Financial Data Analysis (13)Case Study//This course intends to introduce some data mining techniques which include classification, estimation, clustering, and association rules mining. It also provides some application examples for these techniques.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM5803701')
