CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='人因工程心理基礎', course_teacher='紀佳芬', course_type=1, course_discription='心理學概觀、心理的生理基礎、感覺歷程、知覺歷程、學習原理、記憶與遺忘、語言與思考、身心發展、能力及其測量、人格及其測量、動機、壓力、態度、社會行為、心理異常、健康心理、研究法、基本心理歷程之實驗。//1.Master the human information processing model for describing human cognition. <br>2. Evaluate human effort (workload) and human performance under various task conditions. (Signal detection, Path finding, language communication, decision making, manual control and automation).<br>3. Learn the basic concepts of attention, pattern recognition, memory, decision making, learning, training, and stress and human error.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM7301701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='人因工程生理基礎', course_teacher='林久翔', course_type=1, course_discription='能量釋放及來源；肌肉收縮生理學；循環及呼吸系統；工作生理能力；生理能力的評估法；工作生理的應用實例；生理訓練。//This is an advanced ergonomic course for graduate student in industry management. We will examine various factors affecting human physical performance in industries. In the course, the regulatory mechanism of various body functions at rest and during work will be introduced, elementary human anatomy, physiological and biomechanical events will be explained, and most important of all, design and redesign issues of task in the workplaces will be exercised.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM7303701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='存貨理論', course_teacher='曹譽鐘', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程主要涵蓋存貨系統的理論和實務。課程內容包含存貨系統的整體性架構、物料分類和編號、確定性和機率性存貨模式、安全存量之決定、物料需求計劃、批量訂定方法、物流系統探討、物料作業程序和分析、自動化倉儲和電腦化物料管理系統等。課程強調報告和個案討論，並指定電腦作業。研究存貨理論的相關領域及方向亦將在本課程中深入說明。//Inventory control is to manage a list of goods and materials, or those goods and materials themselves, held available in stock by a business. Unless inventory system, we will also study the production, distribution and marketing systems in supply chain. Students can learn the modeling skills, applications and concepts for inventory and supply chain management in this course. Students should be comfortable with mathematical programming and operations research.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM7402701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='品質管制方法', course_teacher='王福琨', course_type=1, course_discription='依課程宗旨，本課程可分：1.品質概念與演進 2.統計方法 3.計量管制圖分析 4.計數管制圖分析 5.短製程管制圖分析 6.製程能力分析 7.實驗設計 8.抽樣檢驗 9.可靠度與失效模式分析 10.田口品質工程等。再以實際案例配合以上主題講解，使學生能靈活運用品管方法以達品質管理之目的//This course is about the use of modern statistical methods for quality control and improvement. It covers a wide range of subjects from basic principles to state-of-the-art techniques, including Modeling Process Quality, Inference about Process Quality, Statistical Process Control, Control Charts, Process Capability Analysis, CUSUM & EWMA, Taguchi\'s Method, Six Sigma, and Other Techniques. The object is to give the students a sound understanding of the principles of quality control.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM9003701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='人性化管理與設計', course_teacher='紀佳芬', course_type=1, course_discription='應用人類的行為、能力、限制和其他特性知識於工具、機器、系統、任務、工作和環境等的設計與評估，以提升各項作業生產力、產品的安全、舒適與功效。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM9007701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='IM'), course_name='服務體驗與管理', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程擬提供服務體驗與管理之概念，使同學具備現代管理者不管是在製造業或服務業上應具備的服務技巧，並進一步引導同學如何應用這些技巧於管理上，以提升企業運作之便利性及企業競爭之優勢，裨使同學對目前業界爭相使用之服務體驗觀察與管理技巧有概略性之認識，能很容易地投身於產業的運作行列中。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=IM9012701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='數量方法─統計方法與資料分析', course_teacher='楊維寧', course_type=1, course_discription='引導學生瞭解統計方法的理論及其應用', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5100701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='財務管理', course_teacher='張光第', course_type=1, course_discription='財務管理乃企業主要功能之一，故為企管學生必須修習之課程。本課程屬概論課程，目的在使學生對財務管理有一全盤性的了解。本課程將對財務管理作全面性的介紹。其內容包括資本預算(投資)決策，融資決策與控制、資本結構與股利政策、資本市場理論與實務、財務規劃、合併與收購決策、風險管理與國際金融市場介紹。//This course examines the financing decision, investment decision, and risk management made by financial manager. What has to be done correctly by managers to enhance the company value is also addressed. Emphasis is place on the concepts and techniques of financial management problems. By applying theory to practical issue, student will conduct real-world cases studies in financial statements analysis, capital budgeting decision and valuation.<br><br>COURSE OBJECTIVES：<br>● To guide student with the understanding of the nature of fundamentals of accounting and financial planning<br><br>● To obtain the skill of financial ratio analysis and dictate the potential flaw on financial statements<br><br>● To learn the capital budgeting decision methods and their relative strengths and weaknesses<br><br>● To understand the meaning of corporate governance and its impact on firm performance<br><br>● To apply valuation methods in estimating company’s intrinsic value', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5300701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='供應鏈管理', course_teacher='周碩彥', course_type=1, course_discription='(1)Introduction to Supply Chain Management (2)Logistics Netowork Configuration (3)Inventory Management and Risk Pooling (4)The Value of Information (5)Supply Chain Integration (6)Strategic Alliances (7)Procurement and Outsourcing Strategies (8)International Issues in Supply Chain Management (9)Coordinated Product and Supply Chain Design (10)Customer Value and Supply Chain  Management (11)Information Technology for Supply Chain Management (12)Decision Support Systems for Supply Chain Management//Exploring fundamental and emerging topics in global supply chain management, including inventory management, network planning, information visibility, supply contract, integration, alliances, procurement, product design, global logistics, risk management, pricing, IT and standards. Contents will be suitable for students pursuing research and/or professional career in this discipline. In addition to the text, simulation games, cases will also be used for presentation and discussion.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5406701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='資訊科技管理', course_teacher='周子銓', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程探討因資訊科技的快速發展，組織所面臨的各項管理上的問題。課程通過個案教學的方式，旨在培養學生從資訊科技實務案例中，學習資訊科技管理所需之專業知識與企業實務，以發展出解決企業問題的能力。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5501701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='策略知識管理', course_teacher='李國光', course_type=1, course_discription='教授知識管理的理論概念與實踐做法，以引導學生對知識管理有正確的認知以及培養實踐知識管理的能力', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5502701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='智能營運', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='因應生產力4.0思維做為台灣產業發展的主軸，產業需要通過ICT技術創造新價值。本課程旨在培育學生了解生產力4.0的思維、關鍵技術發展與應用、商業模式設計、產業轉型等議題，以培育生產力4.0時代高質化產業人才。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5507701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='企業倫理', course_teacher='黃丙喜', course_type=1, course_discription='//Welcome to the join the forum of “Making Ethical Business Decision”. Due to learning is the most valuable moving, we will first try our best to let this forum be a happy journey. <br>Ethic in nothing with mystery, we will not frame business ethics in terms of Aristotle either. As matter of fact, learning about organizational ethics can actually be fun, therefore, we will discuss in this forum about what will be expected of us at General Electric, Bank of America, Formosa, and corporations worldwide, and straight talk about how to manage it responsively, especial when in the period of ethical dilemmas.<br>This forum was developed for the MBA and executive programs of NTUST Management School, and will be relied heavily on the case method of instruction, in which we will jointly analyze, discuss, and learn the fundamentals of what managers do and should do in the world of corporate management; how can they measure ethics, make ethical decisions, and organize their social conducts.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5600701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='人力資源管理個案', course_teacher='葉穎蓉', course_type=1, course_discription='根據哈佛個案教學方法與參與者學習中心的精神，本課程目標係在促進學生們熟悉人力資源管理理論並安排各項個案進行研討，以增強學生掌握人力資源管理技巧的實務操作技巧能耐。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5601701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='行銷資料科學', course_teacher='林孟彥', course_type=1, course_discription='讓學生瞭解資料科學的意義，和大數據的技巧及應用', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5603701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='企業業務溝通技巧與問題解決', course_teacher='翁樸棟', course_type=1, course_discription='隨著科技的進步，尤其是Internet、EC、APP的風起雲湧，各校的商、管學院所無不加強與internet、電子商務、社群經營…等緊密相關之課程，而不知不覺卻忽略了所有商業活動的最基礎元素–「人與人」，管理的範疇：產、銷、人、發、才、資等六大領域，最基礎的就是「人」。  組織為一群個人的組合，共識的產生是組織效率的基本條件；「銷售」表面上似乎是「買」與「賣」的對立…，如何化分散為共識、如何化對立而合作，就都端賴正確的溝通觀念與技巧。「解決問題」是任何工作的核心技能，問題解決的能力已經成為員工最重要的核心職能。但如何真正分辨問題、面對問題、分析問題、解決問題…，這是職場中不論任何人、任何職級都需要有的基本能力。<br> “銷售技巧”不應是狹義的賣方將商品賣給買方；而應該是廣義的：經過良好的溝通，獲得對方的信任，精準地找出對方的需求(待解決的問題)，誠懇地提出最適合的解決方案(解決問題)，促成雙贏的結果。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA5702701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='海外企業研習(一)', course_teacher='何秀青', course_type=1, course_discription='The course aims to introduce students the knowledge learning through the foreign interactions, including the visiting/interview in foreign firms; the academic interactions with foreign universities. The process of oversea trip course also encourage students to organise the visiting agenda by teamwork. The  students\' capabilities in planing, organizing, leading, and controlling will be improved through the activities involvement of the course.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA6001701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='消費者行為', course_teacher='葉明義', course_type=1, course_discription='凡一切與個人或團體獲得、使用、及處置產品、服務、或概念的相關議題，皆屬於消費者行為的範疇。本課程著重於瞭解消費者在思考、感受與其實際取得、使用、或處置的關聯，並探討行銷策略在影響消費者選擇過程中的角色。//Consumer behavior covers the topics of acquisition, use, and disposal of products, services, or ideas for individuals and organizations.  The emphasis is on comprehension of consumer thinking and feeling related to the aforementioned issues as well as an investigation of the impacts of marketing strategies on consumer choices.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA6200701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='生產管理系統', course_teacher='王孔政', course_type=1, course_discription='//To help students become effective managers in today’s competitive, global environment.<br>To help students discover the dynamic field of operations managements.<br>To learn the tools that managers can use to make better operating decisions.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA6400701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='資訊系統與管理', course_teacher='朱宇倩', course_type=1, course_discription='Many businesses look for candidates who know how to use information systems, making a general understanding of information systems an asset to any business student. This course emphasizes on how business objectives shape the application of new information systems and technologies, teaches students how to apply MIS concepts to real-world business scenarios, and helps students strengthen their analytical and decision-making skills.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA6501701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='國際行銷管理', course_teacher='郭五鳳', course_type=1, course_discription='The objective of this course is to enhance graduate students’ knowledge and capability in global marketing management and innovative business strategies. The goals of this course are to understand 1) the dynamic challenges of the global market trend, 2) the up-to-date insights on customer preferences, and 3) the decision making process on value creation, in particular.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA7702701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MA'), course_name='社會科學研究方法', course_teacher='何秀青', course_type=1, course_discription='The course aims to help students to accumulate the knowledge of different methodologies. In order to learn the skills for writing thesis, the course leads students to formulate their ideas, conduct their research question with different methods. Students are expected to learn the techniques to manage a qualitative or a quantitative research in the real researching projects. Students will learn how to work with software and improve the quantitative analysis skills during the process of the course. A final check will be how students complete a research report in social science field or business research.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MA8100701')
