CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='ME'), course_name='動力學', course_teacher='石伊蓓', course_type=0, course_discription='先介紹質點的運動學與運動力學，運動力學包含三種方法，即力、質量與加速度法，功能法，衝量與動量法，其次介紹剛體的運動學與運動力學，分析的運動狀況含平面運動與三維運動。//This course is an introduction to the dynamics and of the particle and rigid body. Topics covered include kinematics and kinetics, including in force-momentum formulation and work-energy concepts for systems of particles and rigid bodies in planar motion. Students will be familiar with the topics of the equations of motion for systems of particles and rigid bodies in planar motion. After this course, students will be able to evaluate kinematics and kinetics of the systems of particles and rigid bodies.<br><br>1.Concepts of engineering dynamics, including in the kinematics and kinetics of particles and rigid bodies.<br>2.The displacements, velocities and accelerations on rectilinear and curvilinear coordinates <br>3.Kinetics: Newton’s law on equation of motions, Work and Energy, and Momentum and Impulse<br>4.The kinematics of particle under force and moment.<br>5.Analytical skills and procedures on kinetics by means of free-body diagram<br>6.Planar kinematics and kinetics of rigid bodies<br>Vibration of single degree-of-freedom system', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=ME3100301')
