CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MG'), course_name='行銷管理', course_teacher='盛麗慧', course_type=1, course_discription='行銷活動為現代企業經營中非常重要的一環，行銷之良窳常為企業經營成敗的關鍵所在。本課程旨在探討行銷的基本概念，行銷環境與機會分析，以及行銷組合策略之規劃與執行。<br>1.行銷概論<br>2.行銷環境分析與行銷資訊系統<br>3.消費者行為，組織購買行為<br>4.產品、價格、促銷、通路策略<br>5.個案研討//1.Marketing: Creating and Capturing Customer Value<br>2.Analyzing the Marketing Environment<br>3.Consumer-Driven Marketing Strategy<br>4.Products, Services, and Brands: Building Customer Value<br>5.New Product Development and Product Life-Cycle Strategies<br>6.Pricing: Understanding and Capturing Customer Value<br>7.Pricing Strategies<br>8.Marketing Channels: Delivering Customer Value<br>9.Retailing and Wholesaling<br>10.Communicating Customer Value: Integrated Marketing Communications Strategy<br>11.Advertising and Public Relations<br>12.Personal Selling and Sales Promotion', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MG5402701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MG'), course_name='管理資訊系統', course_teacher='李國光', course_type=1, course_discription='介紹MIS系統之基本概念以及其應用之考量，以期學生能除了了解MIS為何？包涵了那些子系統外，並能考量爾後MIS使用之環境及時機。<br>本課程主要分下列五部份講授：<br>1.Foundations of Information Technology<br>2.Information Systems Technology<br>3.Information Systems Development<br>4.Information Support Systems<br>5.Managing Information Technology//Competitive advantage is an advantage over competitors in some measure such as cost, quality, or speed; it leads to control of a market and to larger-than-average profits. Many organizations achieve competitive advantage through strategic information systems. Therefore, becoming knowledgeable about how strategic information systems impact strategy and competitive position is very important. The course will cover the following topics:<br><br>1. Competitive environment and paradigm shift<br>2. What is Management Information Systems?<br>3. The evolving role of Information systems<br>4. What is Strategic Information Systems Planning?<br>5. Models for strategic information systems planning<br>6. Establishing the strategic information systems planning process<br>7. What is Organizational Reengineering?<br>8. Models for organizational reengineering<br>9. Implementation of organizational reengineering', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MG5403701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MG'), course_name='組織與管理', course_teacher='鄭仁偉', course_type=1, course_discription='課程在於使同學了解管理思想之演進，組織與管理之重要理論，未來發展趨勢，及理論與實務之配合技巧等，課程主要目標為：<br>1.培養管理哲學和觀念<br>2.以分組個案研究方式加強分析、解決問題及決策能力。<br>3.訓練企劃案及其他書面報告之寫作技巧<br>4.塑造管理人員應具備的信念、特質、意志及工作倫理//Organization and Management introduce the foundations of organization theories,and the influence of system-level variables on the critical determinants of organization effectiveness and efficiency.The organization design and mechanism will affect employee’s productivity,absenteeism,turnover,job satisfaction, and organizational citizenship. Students will learn how to design organization,and know how to make the organization operating more efficiently.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MG5404701')
