CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MG'), course_name='海外企業經營實務(一)', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程介紹國內企業進行全球佈局時，在亞洲各國所面臨之各項挑戰與因應對策。其中包括：<br>1.中國大陸台商經營之挑戰<br>2.台商在東南亞（大陸、越南、新加坡、馬來西亞、印尼等國家）經營策略//This course introduces the challenges Taiwanese enterprises are facing when they enter foreign countries, such as mainland China, Vietnam, Singapore, Malaysia, and Indonesia. This course also explains the strategic strategies to cope these challenges.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MG6704701')
