CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MG'), course_name='統計資料分析與應用', course_teacher='楊維寧', course_type=1, course_discription='1.利用機率模型描述樣本數據與隨機現象。<br>2.經由樣本數據推論母體參數。<br>3.利用機率敘述量化抽樣誤差，包括區間估計與假設檢定。<br>4.利用電腦模擬瞭解隨機現象與強化學習效果。//1. Use probability models to describe the data and model random phenomenen.<br>2. Make statistical inferences about the population parameters based on the sample information.<br>3. Quantify the sampling errors through probability statements --- interval estimation and hypothesis testing.<br>4. Understand random phenomenen and strengthen pedagogic effect using computer simulations.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MG7001701')
