CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='應用程式語言', course_teacher='陳文川', course_type=1, course_discription='VB和Object-Oriented Approach介紹、專案檔、表單和控制項、事件模式、決策流程、鍵盤與滑鼠事件、繪圖、陣列與副程式、模組與專案、循序檔與隨機檔、資料庫、多媒體。//This course focuses on the programming skills of Visual Basic .Net in terms of basic process, common controls, menus and dialog boxes, keyboard and mouse events, array and subroutine, database programming, application development for mobile devices. Each chapter is introduced from the easy to the difficult and complicated; moreover, it is supplemented by some examples of daily life. The objective of this course makes beginners easy to learn and the possession of skills can be a basis for future advanced applications.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI2202701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資料結構', course_teacher='林伯慎', course_type=0, course_discription='著重針對不同類型之問題，選擇適當之資料結構，可以簡化處理步驟，因為該課程之習題以PASCAL（或C）語言寫程式較容易。先介紹一般簡單型資料結構，如整數、實數、字串、陣列、集合、資料檔並輔以PASCAL（或C）語言介紹，然後介紹抽象之資料結構包括鏈結串列（list）堆疊、佇列、樹列結構，另先介紹資料結構與演算法之關係及遞迴處理。//Data structure is the basic training for programming. It describes how the data in real world are represented and accessed in computers typically based on which the algorithms can be written. In this course, the topics about stack, queue, list, table, tree, and graph are introduced, and example codes are given in C language.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI3002301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='管理數學', course_teacher='洪政煌', course_type=0, course_discription='//1.Solving Ax = b for square systems by elimination (pivots, multipliers,back substitution, invertibility of A, factorization into A = LU)<br>2.Complete solution to Ax = b (column space containing b, rank of A,nullspace of A and special solutions to Ax = 0 from row reduced R)<br>3.Basis and dimension (bases for the four fundamental subspaces)<br>4.Least squares solutions (closest line by understanding projections)<br>5.Orthogonalization by Gram-Schmidt (factorization into A = QR)<br>6.Properties of determinants (leading to the cofactor formula and the sum over all n! permutations, applications to inv(A) and volume)<br>7.Eigenvalues and eigenvectors (diagonalizing A, computing powers A^k and matrix exponentials to solve difference and differential equations)<br>8.Symmetric matrices and positive definite matrices (real eigenvalues and orthogonal eigenvectors, tests for x\'Ax > 0, applications)<br>9.Linear transformations and change of basis (connected to the Singular Value Decomposition -- orthonormal bases that diagonalize A)', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI3008301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊安全導論', course_teacher='吳宗成', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程包括以下主題：<br>第一部份：基礎篇<br>資訊安全概論、密碼學概論<br>第二部份：應用篇<br>系統安全、資訊安全管理、網路安全、電子商務安全、<br>資訊安全法律<br>第三部份：進階篇<br>資料庫安全、多媒體安全、無線網路安全//This course includes the following three parts:<br>Part I: Basics<br>Concepts & terminologies of information security and cryptography<br>Part II: Applications<br>System security, Information management, Network security,<br>E-commerce security, Legal systems for information security<br>Part III: Advanced<br>Database security, Multimedia security, Wireless security', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI3013701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊安全管理', course_teacher='查士朝', course_type=1, course_discription='課程預計包括以下內容：資訊安全風險評估之方法；風險的管理與監控；缺失的矯正與預防；管理者的責任；資訊安全政策的擬定；資訊安全組織的建立；實體安全管理程序；意外與問題管理程序；資產管理程序；人員安全管理程序；通訊及作業安全管理程序；存取控制管理程序；業務永續運作管理程序；資訊安全稽核管理程序；以及與資訊治理程序的整合的。//This course will cover the following content: (1) What is security? (2) Security risk assessment and management (3) Corrective and preventative controls (4) Management responsibilities (5) Security policy (6) Security Organization (7) Asset management procedures (8) Incidents and problems management process (9) Physical security (9) Human resource security (10) Communication and operational management processes (11) Access control (12) Information system acquisition, development, and maintenance (13) Business continuity planning (14) Security auditing (15) Information security and IT governance', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI3016701')
