CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊網路', course_teacher='賴源正', course_type=0, course_discription='本課程包含傳授基本傳送，交換機的概念，ISO開放式網路架構，區域網路與廣域網路及相關之網路系統，如TCP/IP，X.25，ISDN等。//This course is an introduction to networks. It will explore the technology, applications, and standards of networks. This course covers why and how various protocols and algorithms are designed. Course materials for each chapter (slides) are downloadable from the course homepage.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI4206301')
