CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='高等演算法', course_teacher='徐俊傑', course_type=1, course_discription='演算法是撰寫程式開發軟體最重要的基礎，演算法可以幫助程式開發者或系統分析師設計方法解決所面對的程式開發問題，使得所開發出來的軟體更有效率。//The content of the course includes the introduction of computer algorithms, how to analyze program performance, data structures, divide-and-conquer, greedy method, dynamic programming, search techniques, backtracking, and branch-and bound。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5109701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='電子化企業', course_teacher='魏小蘭', course_type=1, course_discription='在Internet時代，如何建立一個具競爭力的電子化企業，成為資管領域重要的議題。本課程介紹電子化企業相關的基本概念，以及企業如何利用網際網路及各種整合型的資訊系統，將企業內部價值鏈及外部各種跨組織活動，進行連結與整合，以提升其競爭力。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5112701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='網路服務資訊安全', course_teacher='羅乃維', course_type=1, course_discription='網路服務(Web Services)為具體實踐服務導向架構（SOA）的關鍵技術；如何保護網路服務提供者與網路服務使用者雙方的資訊安全實為網路服務應用發展的一個基本且重要的課題。本課程之目的為使學生了解網路服務技術及其發展方向、網路服務所面臨的資安威脅、以及對應發展出的安全標準與資安防禦方法，進而使學生具備對網路服務與應用的各項資安議題與防禦技術的知識。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5117701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='服務導向企業系統管理', course_teacher='魏小蘭', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程主要由組織、管理、技術等不同的理論觀點分析與探討服務導向企業系統的管理議題，並瞭解如何應用服務導向企業系統增加企業的價值。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5215701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='數量方法─統計方法與資料分析', course_teacher='楊維寧', course_type=1, course_discription='引導學生瞭解統計方法的理論及其應用', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5217701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='創新與企業家精神', course_teacher='羅台生', course_type=1, course_discription='這門課將結合理論與實務，來瞭解創新與企業家精神。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5224701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='智能營運', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='因應生產力4.0思維做為台灣產業發展的主軸，產業需要通過ICT技術創造新價值。本課程旨在培育學生了解生產力4.0的思維、關鍵技術發展與應用、商業模式設計、產業轉型等議題，以培育生產力4.0時代高質化產業人才。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5226701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='多媒體系統', course_teacher='楊傳凱', course_type=1, course_discription='講授多媒體資訊系統之概念架構﹑發展方法及推廣應用。//Chapter1  Introduction<br>Chapter2 Enabling technologies<br>Chapter3 Introduction to computer graphics<br>Chapter4 Vector graphics<br>Chapter5 Bitmapped images<br>Chapter6 Color<br>Chapter7 Characters and fonts<br>Chapter8 Layout<br>Chapter9 Hypertext<br>Chapter10 Video<br>Chapter11 Animation<br>Chapter12 Sound<br>Chapter13 Combining media<br>Chapter14 Events, scripts and interactivity<br>Chapter15 Multimedia and networks<br># Huffman Coding, from "Data Compresssion: Principles and Applications", by Prof. Kuo-Liang Chung<br># Arithmetic Coding, from "Data Compresssion: Principles and Applications", by Prof. Kuo-Liang Chung<br># Lossless Compression, from "Data Compresssion: Principles and Applications", by Prof. Kuo-Liang Chung<br># Wavelet, from "Data Compresssion: Principles and Applications", by Prof. Kuo-Liang Chung<br># Image Watermarking, by Prof. Chiou-Ting Hsu at NTHU<br># Fractal Compression<br># Transferring Color to Greyscale Images, by Tom Welsh et al. in Siggraph 2002 (paper)<br># Digital Image Inpainting, by Manuel Oliveira et al. in VIIP2001 (paper)<br># Image Morphing<br># Object Tracking in Images and Video<br># Optical Character Recognition<br># Introduction to Volume Visualization, by Klaus Mueller', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5300701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊科技管理', course_teacher='周子銓', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程探討因資訊科技的快速發展，組織所面臨的各項管理上的問題。//The key Challenge facing today\'s corporate is what a corporate should do to succeed in a highly uncertain and dynamic market place today. Strategic Knowledge Management enables an organization to combine its knowledge on markets and products with change adaptation knowledge to gain sustainable competitive advantage. The course will cover the following topics:<br>1.What is Knowledge?<br>2.Knowledge Audit<br>3.What is Knowledge Management?<br>4.Mentor Model and Knowledge<br>5.What is Strategic Knowledge Management?<br>6.Systems Thinking and ST Diagram<br>7.Knowledge Management Development Model<br>8.Tools and Software', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5303701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊系統與管理', course_teacher='朱宇倩', course_type=1, course_discription='Many businesses look for candidates who know how to use information systems, making a general understanding of information systems an asset to any business student. This course emphasizes on how business objectives shape the application of new information systems and technologies, teaches students how to apply MIS concepts to real-world business scenarios, and helps students strengthen their analytical and decision-making skills.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5309701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='策略知識管理', course_teacher='李國光', course_type=1, course_discription='//Course will explain the significance of knowledge management and specific practices to promote knowledge management. In addition, the course will also be required for business executives, and the concept of knowledge management strategy and development model to assist executives in the strategic management process, the effective practice of knowledge management practices. Operation depends on effective knowledge management system tools, this course will also introduce the concept map, VenSim systems thinking tools.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5410701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='網路流量模式與應用', course_teacher='洪政煌', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程將涵蓋以下內容：1.網路模式之基本介紹及定義，2.最短路徑問題，3.最大流量問題，4.最小成本流量，5.指派問題，6.匹配問題，7.最小擴張樹問題，8.多元商品流量問題，9.推銷員問題，10.網路設計問題。以上每單元並配合相關模式應用之個案分析及討論，介紹個案之主要來源為物流、運籌及供應鍊管理。//This course will cover the following content: the definition and introduction of network model, the shortest path problem, maximum flow problem, minimum cost flow problem, assignment problem, matching problem, minimum spanning tree problem, multicommodity problem, traveling salesman problem, and network design problem.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5413701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='科技與法律', course_teacher='陳曉慧', course_type=1, course_discription='其主要之課程單元如下：<br>1.智慧財產之保護與科技產業發展<br>2.掌握全球資訊基礎建設上的商機 <br>3.因應生醫產業發展所需法律與倫理規劃//This course involves 3 main units below：<br>1. Intellectual Property (IP) and Technology Industry<br>2. Seizing the Business Opportunities on the Global <br>3. Compliance with The Legal & Ethical Governance that Supports the Biomedical Industrial Development', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5510701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='科技與創新管理', course_teacher='陳正綱', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程首先介紹科技管理概論、包括科學、科技、創新、發明與管理的本質與其相互之間的關係，接著探討如何以策略性科技管理來創造企業核心競爭力以營造競爭優勢，並從產品發展週期之觀點來審視如何實施創新管理；接下來將介紹一些屬於科技變動管理的議題，如：科技的取代與擴散、科技變動的預測、科技的移轉與創新的評估…等；最後，探討科技研究與發展的策略與科技政策與社會環境的相關議題。希望學員們從本課程的修習中，擴大對科技創新的活動與管理功能的認識，進一步能整合科技與管理以創造企業經營的競爭優勢。//This course introduces Technology Management Studies, including the relationship between the nature of science, technology, innovation, invention and its management between each other, and then discuss how to create a strategic technology management core competitiveness of enterprises in order to create a competitive advantage, and from product development view cycles to examine how to implement innovation management; next will introduce some of the issues are technological change management, such as: technology substitution and diffusion prediction technology changes, transfer of technology and innovation in assessment, etc; and finally, to explore science and technology strategy and technology policy issues related to the environment and society research and development. I hope to attend this course from students, the expansion of the activities of scientific and technological innovation and knowledge management capabilities, and further integration of technology and management in order to be able to create a competitive advantage in business.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5512701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='電子商務', course_teacher='徐慧霞', course_type=1, course_discription='//The course is focused on three areas, namely: e-commerce, e-business and Internet marketing, content and e-commerce in order to present business environment in the important role played. E-commerce is an enabling technology that can increase the accuracy of business transactions and effectiveness in business. The impact of e-commerce will slow us every aspect of life, large to the National Act, economic, policy and trade, as small as the market mechanism, competition mode, the transaction level and consumption patterns and so on. Hope that students of this course on e-commerce and e-commerce transactions have a better understanding of the environment. E-commerce transaction platform that the media, so that they may simplify transaction procedures, logistics planning information transparent and efficient overall supply chain effectiveness.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5601701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊管理專題研討', course_teacher='楊傳凱', course_type=0, course_discription='為提昇研究生對資管領域多面性之認識，以期能激發研究之興趣與跨領域之整合。//Scientists, researchers, industry professionals, professors, and experts from other fields are invited to present their latest work or research findings. Students taking this course are required to <br>(1)write a summary report on each presentation,<br>(2)participate in group discussion,<br>(3)present their work and research findings to others', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5908301')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='資訊安全與計量運算專題研究(一)', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程主要內容是由研究生依據所選定之研究主題，進行廣泛的文獻收集、閱讀、分析與彙整，並向授課教授提出論文研讀心得報告，經由與其它修課研究生與授課教授的互動討論，期能找出好的研究問題，並能針對此研究問題之背景、動機、重要性、研究方法、研究步驟、困難點與因應方式、驗證、研究成果之應用與意涵等，提出完整的論文研究計畫書。研究議題則著重「資訊安全」與「計量運算」之研究，「資訊安全」包含針對密碼學 (Cryptography)、密碼分析 (Cryptanalysis)、風險管理 (Risk Management)、身份與存取管理 (Identity and Access Management) 等現代資訊安全的重要議題。「計量運算」則包含網路流量模型與應用 (Network Flow Model and Applications)、蒙地卡羅方法 (Monte Carlo Methods)、資訊經濟 (Information Economics)、決策分析 (Decision Analysis)、系統模擬 (System Simulation)、作業研究 (Operations Research)、定價 (Pricing) 等量化研究所需的方法與議題。//This course aims to equip graduate students with the ability of independent academic research, including the literature review, problem identification, research methods, discussion and implication of research results, academic article writing, etc., by attending the regular meetings with peer graduate students and their supervisors. The topics covered include “Information Security” and “Quantitative Computing.”', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5910701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='多媒體專題研究(一)', course_teacher='多位教師', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程共計將研討以下進階多媒體專題。1. 視訊摘要，2. 顏色反量化，3. 音樂視覺化，4. 文字及影像音樂化，5. 視訊動作擷取，6. 多媒體風格化及個人化，7. 語音與手勢辨識，8. 多媒體資訊檢索，9. 聲訊視訊整合，10. 多模式互動與交談。//This course will study the following advanced multimedia topics:1. Video summary, 2. Color de-quantization, 3. Music visualization, 4. Text and image sonification, 5. Motion capture by videos, 6. Multimedia stylization and personalization, 7. Speech and gesture recognition, 8. Multimedia information retrieval, 9. Audio visual integration, 10. Multimodal interaction and dialogue.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5913701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='MI'), course_name='演算法專題研究(一)', course_teacher='徐俊傑', course_type=1, course_discription='本課程將研討以下進階演算法專題： 1. 複雜度分析，2. 貪婪法，3. 各個擊破法，4. 動態規劃，5. 切割與搜尋，6. 樹狀搜尋，7. NP-completeness，8. 圖學理論，9. 連結網路。//This course will study the following advanced algorithm topics: 1. complexity analysis, 2. greedy method, 3. divide-and-conquer, 4. dynamic programming, 5. prune-and-search, 6. tree search, 7. NP-completeness, 8. graph theory, 9. interconnection network.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=MI5916701')
