CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='PA'), course_name='專利檢索與方法論', course_teacher='管中徽', course_type=1, course_discription='專利檢索係從專利資料庫搜尋出符合特定目的的相關專利的程序。為了掌握競爭對手的研發動態、瞭解特定技術領域的發展、專利申請前搜尋相關前案、產品研發上市前避免侵權等，都需要從事專利檢索來收集相關的專利。專利檢索因此是研究人員與從事專利業務的人員必備的技能。<br>Patent search is a process of locating a set of patents from patent databases that are relevant to a specific purpose. In order capture a competitor’s R&D status, discover a technology field’s progress, find related prior arts before filing patent application, to avoid infringement before R&D or product lauch, etc., people usually have to conduct patent search to find the related patents. Patent search therefore is a skill that researchers and patent professionals must require.<br><br>專利檢索常被認為是一種藝術、而非科學，但實際上專利檢索其實是可以被系統化與科學化的處理的。這門課就在導引同學如何掌握專利檢索的系統化與科學化的方法。<br>Patent search is often considered more of an art than science. But patent search can be conducted in a systematic and scientific manner. This course therefore will guide students in mastering these systematic and scientific skills.<br><br>專利檢索主要倚賴的是所謂的書目（bibliographic）資料，也就是在行政程序中由申請人提出或由權責機關賦予的資料，例如申請日號、公告日號、引用與被引用資訊、優先權、專利分類等。本課程將教示如何系統化、科學化地利用專利書目資訊來進行成功的專利檢索。<br>Patent search mostly relies on the so-called patent bibliometric data which is provided by the applicant or by the patent authority during the prosecution of the patent application, such as the application date/number, issued date/number, cited and citing information, priority, patent classifications, etc. This course therefore will let the students practice how to systematically and scientifically utilize patent bibliometric data to achieve su', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=PA5142701')
CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='PA'), course_name='智慧財產鑑價方法', course_teacher='蔡鴻文', course_type=1, course_discription='智慧財產的商業模式，要著重在實施跟交換，而商業模式中獲利最大的是在商品化、產業化，再來就是各種交換（股票、損害賠償金、權利金等）。商品化和產業化，是智慧財產權獲利最大的兩種模式。<br><br>    本課程會先介紹智慧財產商業模式的意義與發展，然後再進入商業模式的介紹，以智慧財產評價為主題進行闡述與案例討論，提供同學智慧財產加值分析能力與智慧財產策略之規劃能力。', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=PA5143701')
