CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='PE'), course_name='體育(流行舞蹈[3])', course_teacher='邱淑媛', course_type=1, course_discription='課程目標:<br>1.維持良好的身體組成。<br>2.建立”養成運動習慣 “觀念。<br>3.培養終身從事休閒運動。<br><br>課程內容包括：<br>介紹各式各樣的舞蹈課程;ex:流行舞蹈、基本動作、組合動作、舞蹈小品(HIP-HOP、Stree dance、Reggar、African dance、New Jazz)、表演與欣賞等。<br><br>教學要點：<br>1.示範教學法<br>2.分組練習法<br>3.創意教學法<br>4.合作學習法<br>5.趣味、基礎、友誼教學法//Goal：<br>1.To keep good body composition.<br>2.The establishment"s cultivate and exercise and make it a rule" the idea.<br>3.Develop to work on the leisure exercise life long.<br>Teaching program :<br>Curriculum key point: Cardio, Strength and Mind/Body, offering a chance to sample a selection of our popular and very diverse students programs. Orientation features an introduction to the various dance classes; discussions on dance’s equipment and technique; demonstrations, as well as opportunities to have a go.<br><br>Essentials of Teaching：<br>1.Example teaching approach <br>2.To practice divide into groups <br>3.Creative teaching approach <br>4.Cooperative learning approach <br>5.Fun, fundamental and friendship approach', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=PE1333754')
