CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='TC'), course_name='活力合唱（一）', course_teacher='王維君', course_type=0, course_discription='(1)開發學生聲音潛能。<br>(2)提供基本合唱技巧訓練。<br>(3)欣賞東西方經典合唱作品與著名團體。<br>(4)演練不同風格的合唱歌曲。<br>(5)指導學生發表改編或創作合唱歌曲。//This course is designed as follows:<br>(1)Developing individual abilities of vocal singing. <br>(2)Learning basic techniques of choral singing.<br>(3)Learning how to evaluate eastern and western choral<br>   masterworks and famous choirs.<br>(4)Rehearsing various types of choral works.<br>(5)Advising students’ arrangements or compositions of<br>   choral songs.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=TCG003301')
