CourseInformation.objects.create(course_administrator=CourseAdminstrator.objects.get(admin_id='TC'), course_name='國際禮儀', course_teacher='郭天明', course_type=0, course_discription='培養學生國際化之禮儀內涵，使學生能了解相敬如賓待人之道及正確運用國際禮儀相<br>關規範，並藉由課程了解不同國家、種族、宗教的國際禮儀相關事務，達到彼此尊<br>重、和諧相處，以塑造個人之優質形象。<br>In response to international trend, knowing when to act and when not to, cultivating the capabilities of diplomatic skills and public relationship, and promoting national competitiveness is the core course for new generations.<br>This course includes the fields of dining, eating, dressing, living, and transportation from daily life to cultivate student\'s basic etiquette. In this class, students can learn and practice their charm using active and positive attitude, and realize international etiquette is the equipped basic knowledge for modern citizens, especially when they are on-job during their career journey.', course_website='http://info.ntust.edu.tw/faith/edua/app/qry_linkoutline.aspx?semester=1071&courseno=TCG056301')
